%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jio%20IPO%20may%20slip%20to%20second%20half%20of%20FY27%20on%20geopolitical%20risks%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777449123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-11%2F07%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F1200X628%2F1762485056-8596.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjio-ipo-may-slip-to-second-half-of-fy27-on-geopolitical-risks-report-126042900568_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Earlier%20market%20rumors%20reported%20that%20the%20IPO%20could%20come%20as%20early%20as%20May%2C%20with%20Reliance%20looking%20to%20shed%202.5-3%20per%20cent%20stake%20from%20its%20existing%2067%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Jio%20for%20close%20to%20%244%20billion%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjio-ipo-may-slip-to-second-half-of-fy27-on-geopolitical-risks-report-126042900568_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjio-ipo-may-slip-to-second-half-of-fy27-on-geopolitical-risks-report-126042900568_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjio-ipo-may-slip-to-second-half-of-fy27-on-geopolitical-risks-report-126042900568_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20key%20oil%20producer%20is%20quitting%20OPEC%20at%20a%20critical%20moment%20for%20the%20market%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227664%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20headquarters%20of%20the%20Organization%20of%20the%20Petroleum%20Exporting%20Countries%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f17c469244129ecb2f9212%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225095%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20UAE's%20decision%20to%20quit%20OPEC%20could%20reshape%20how%20the%20group%20influences%20global%20oil%20supply.%3Cp%3EOPEC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20UAE%20is%20quitting%20OPEC%20after%20nearly%2060%20years%20amid%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20for%20global%20energy%20markets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20signals%20the%20UAE%20will%20have%20more%20freedom%20to%20ramp%20up%20oil%20production%20as%20its%20strategy%20shifts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20exit%20could%20weaken%20OPEC's%20grip%20on%20supply%20%E2%80%94%20and%20raises%20the%20risk%20of%20further%20fractures%20within%20the%20cartel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20oil%20producer%20is%20walking%20away%20from%20the%20Organization%20of%20the%20Petroleum%20Exporting%20Countries%20at%20a%20critical%20moment%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-iran-war-trump-wti-brent-futures-ceasefire-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eglobal%20energy%20markets.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20announced%20it%20will%20withdraw%20from%20the%20organization%20on%20May%201.%20This%20ends%20nearly%20six%20decades%20of%20membership%20and%20deals%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20oil%20producers'%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20reflects%20a%20growing%20tension%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20OPEC%3A%20Producers%20with%20spare%20capacity%20are%20increasingly%20constrained%20by%20quotas%20as%20the%20global%20energy%20landscape%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20demand%20nearing%20a%20peak%2C%20the%20calculation%20for%20producers%20with%20low-cost%20barrels%20is%20changing%20fast%2C%20and%20waiting%20your%20turn%20inside%20a%20quota%20system%20starts%20to%20look%20like%20leaving%20money%20on%20the%20table%2C%26quot%3B%20Jorge%20Leon%2C%20head%20of%20geopolitical%20analysis%20at%20Rystad%20Energy%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20disruptions%20linked%20to%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20the%20UAE%20was%20producing%20about%203.4%20million%20barrels%20per%20day%E2%80%94%20well%20below%20its%20capacity%20of%204.8%20million%20barrels%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20framed%20the%20exit%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20strategic%20pivot.%20It%20said%20the%20decision%20reflects%20its%20%26quot%3Blong-term%20strategic%20and%20economic%20vision%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20evolving%20energy%20profile%2C%20while%20signaling%20plans%20to%20expand%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20is%20striking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobal%20oil%20markets%20are%20already%20under%20intense%20strain%20due%20to%20a%20war%20involving%20Iran%20that%20has%20severely%20disrupted%20flows%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraffic-appears-to-halt-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20critical%20chokepoint%20that%20normally%20handles%20about%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20world's%20seaborne%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20supply%20shock%20has%20kept%20oil%20prices%20high%2C%20muting%20the%20immediate%20market%20impact%20of%20the%20UAE's%20future%20oil%20supply%20boost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20this%20can%20be%20tapped%2C%20there%20must%20be%20a%20resolution%20in%20the%20Persian%20Gulf%20that%20allows%20for%20uninhibited%20energy%20flows%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20once%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20ING's%20commodity%20strategists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternational%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBrent%20crude%20oil%20futures%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%200.3%25%20higher%20at%20%24111.64%20per%20barrel%20at%201%3A55%20a.m.%20ET%20on%20Wednesday.%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWest%20Texas%20Intermediate%3C%2Fa%3E%20oil%20futures%20were%200.2%25%20lower%20at%20%2499.73%20per%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20departure%20also%20weakens%20OPEC%20itself.%20As%20one%20of%20the%20group's%20largest%20producers%2C%20the%20UAE's%20exit%20reduces%20the%20group's%20ability%20to%20coordinate%20supply%20and%20influence%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20also%20raises%20the%20prospect%20of%20further%20fractures%20within%20the%20cartel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20certainly%20be%20welcomed%20by%20President%20Trump%2C%20as%20it%20erodes%20OPEC's%20influence%20in%20the%20oil%20market%2C%20while%20it%20should%20also%20be%20beneficial%20for%20importers%20and%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20commodity%20strategists%20at%20ING%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20another%20key%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20UAE's%20exit%20could%20trigger%20further%20fractures%20among%20remaining%20OPEC%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuae-exits-opec-global-oil-markets-supply-price-impact-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777448467000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f17c5b9244129ecb2f9213%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuae-exits-opec-global-oil-markets-supply-price-impact-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20has%20announced%20it%20will%20withdraw%20from%20the%20cartel%20on%20May%201%2C%20ending%20nearly%20six%20decades%20of%20membership%20in%20the%20powerful%20cartel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Cursor%20developer%20says%20engineers%20need%20to%20set%20'clear%20expectations'%20as%20AI%20lets%20product%20managers%20build%20prototypes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cursor%20logo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f190f93b4f7c3af2b7aec8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEric%20Zakariasson%2C%20an%20engineer%20at%20Cursor%2C%20said%20that%20AI%20is%20enabling%20product%20managers%20to%20build%20prototypes%20more%20easily.%3Cp%3ESamuel%20Boivin%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Cursor%20engineer%20says%20AI%20tools%20let%20product%20managers%20build%20prototypes%20without%20backend%20systems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20engineers%20should%20set%20%26quot%3Bclear%20expectations%26quot%3B%20to%20improve%20the%20workflow%2C%20says%20Eric%20Zakariasson.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20comments%20come%20as%20the%20role%20of%20product%20managers%20and%20engineers%20shifts%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20product%20managers%20are%20spinning%20up%20prototypes%20with%20AI-assisted%20coding%20tools%2C%20engineers%20are%20left%20to%20make%20them%20production-ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Zakariasson%2C%20an%20engineer%20at%20Cursor%20who%20focuses%20on%20developer%20experience%20and%20product%2C%20said%20at%20the%20AI%20Engineer%20Europe%202026%20conference%20in%20a%20recording%20published%20Tuesday%20that%20setting%20%26quot%3Bclear%20expectations%26quot%3B%20between%20engineering%20and%20product%20teams%20could%20help%20smooth%20workflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20includes%20defining%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20engineers%20kind%20of%20want%20from%20the%20product%20organization%20and%20what's%20most%20helpful%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20not%20vibe%20coding%20complete%20SaaS%20products%20is%20the%20most%20efficient%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20fully%20functioning%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZakariasson%20said%20product%20managers%20can%20now%20create%20interactive%20prototypes%20without%20touching%20backend%20systems%20using%20AI-assisted%20coding%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20prototypes%20can%20show%20how%20a%20product%20should%20behave%20%E2%80%94%20what%20happens%20when%20a%20user%20clicks%20a%20button%20or%20submits%20a%20form.%20However%2C%20these%20products%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20fully%20working%2C%20%26quot%3Bjust%20enough%2C%20to%20like%2C%20your%20engineers%20can%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20Zakariasson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279f9aa1a-1b55-4f9a-bc60-83b7888adc21%5C%22%3EProduct%20managers%20become%20AI%20builders%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProduct%20managers%20are%20increasingly%20expected%20to%20build%20their%20own%20prototypes%2C%20experimenting%20with%20vibe%20coding%20as%20the%20lines%20between%20product%20and%20engineering%20blur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%20in%20February%20that%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-pms-ai-builders-tech-industry-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20product%20managers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20started%20calling%20themselves%20%26quot%3BAI%20builders%2C%26quot%3B%20reflecting%20how%20AI%20coding%20tools%20are%20expanding%20who%20can%20build%20software%20inside%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20also%20comes%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-q4-2025-earnings-ai-investments-capex-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebroader%20leadership%20push%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20Meta's%20Q4%202025%20earnings%20call%2C%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20said%20AI%20tools%20would%20fundamentally%20change%20how%20work%20gets%20done%20across%20the%20company%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20investing%20in%20AI-native%20tooling%2C%20so%20individuals%20at%20Meta%20can%20get%20more%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20elevating%20individual%20contributors%20and%20flattening%20teams.%20We're%20starting%20to%20see%20projects%20that%20used%20to%20require%20big%20teams%20now%20be%20accomplished%20by%20a%20single%20very%20talented%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20companies%20are%20also%20rethinking%20traditional%20roles.%20Last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-product-manager-apm-full-stack-builder-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20scrap%20its%20associate%20product%20manager%20program%20and%20replace%20it%20with%20training%20focused%20on%20coding%2C%20design%2C%20and%20end-to-end%20product%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20tools%20are%20changing%20what%20product%20managers%20can%20do%2C%20some%20engineers%20say%20AI-assisted%20coding%20is%20making%20their%20jobs%20more%20demanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiddhant%20Khare%2C%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20ONA%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20February%20that%20although%20AI%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-fatigue-burnout-software-engineer-essay-siddhant-khare-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboosted%20his%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20has%20also%20changed%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20used%20to%20call%20it%20an%20engineer%2C%20now%20it%20is%20like%20a%20reviewer%2C%26quot%3B%20Khare%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20you%20are%20a%20judge%20at%20an%20assembly%20line%20and%20that%20assembly%20line%20is%20never-ending%2C%20you%20just%20keep%20stamping%20those%20PRs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20AI-generated%20code%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproduct-manager-ai-builder-prototypes-cursor-engineer-clear-expectations-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777448197000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f191369244129ecb2f9237%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproduct-manager-ai-builder-prototypes-cursor-engineer-clear-expectations-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20product%20managers%20build%20prototypes%20with%20AI%2C%20a%20Cursor%20de