insider.com%2Famerican-mom-in-japan-parenting-is-easier-here-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebecoming%20a%20mother%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20bakery%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20handles%20the%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It's%20great%20to%20the%20most%20recently%20recently.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f026d5367066d7c2971b3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOnoda's%20husband%20REWRITE%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Rei%20Onoda%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20opened%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago.%20At%20first%2C%20most%20customers%20were%20local.%20After%20about%206%20months%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emore%20tourists%20started%20coming%2C%20finding%20out%20about%20us%20through%20Instagram%20and%20Google%20Maps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20day%2C%20I%20bake%20a%20handful%20of%20loaves%20%E2%80%94%20country-style%2C%20sandwich%20bread%2C%20and%20rye%20%E2%80%94%20and%20prepare%20cakes%20and%20cookies%20at%20the%20start%20of%20each%20week.%20We%20usually%20see%20around%2015%20groups%20on%20weekdays%20and%20closer%20to%2025%20on%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalancing%20the%20bakery%20and%20motherhood%20has%20been%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mother%20and%20child%20in%20a%20house%20in%20Japan.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f01df33fecbb42897a4c1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOnoda%20found%20balancing%20the%20bakery%20and%20motherhood%20challenging.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Rei%20Onoda%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20learned%20to%20rely%20on%20others.%20With%20support%20from%20my%20husband's%20parents%20and%20daycare%2C%20I%20began%20to%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20asking%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20