became%20the%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20bakery%20exists%20because%20of%20the%20support%20we%20received%20from%20the%20local%20community.%20I%20hope%20that%20as%20my%20son%20grows%20up%2C%20he'll%20see%20that%20and%20understand%20the%20value%20of%20building%20something%20with%20others%20and%20not%20giving%20up%20on%20what%20you%20believe%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-attendant-quit-job-moved-tokyo-akiya-bakery-rural-japan-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777435605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f02508367066d7c2971b38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-attendant-quit-job-moved-tokyo-akiya-bakery-rural-japan-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rei%20Onoda%20bought%20a%20%2450%2C000%20abandoned%20home%20in%20rural%20Japan%20while%20pregnant%20%E2%80%94%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20quit%20their%20jobs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22akarplus%40insider.com%20(Alexandra%20Karplus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20proposes%20rules%20to%20allow%20higher%20ethanol-blended%20fuels%20in%20vehicles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777435553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-03%2F09%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F1200X628%2F1773075095-0235.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fcentre-proposes-rules-to-allow-higher-ethanol-blended-fuels-in-vehicles-126042900150_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20said%20the%20draft%20includes%20provisions%20for%20E85%20fuel%2C%20a%20blend%20of%20%E2%80%8C85%25%20ethanol%20with%20petrol%2C%20and%20E100%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20vehicles%20to%