%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20shrimp%20alfredo%20and%20garlic%20shrimp%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f166299244129ecb2f91e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERed%20Lobster%20brought%20back%20its%20Endless%20Shrimp%20promotion%20on%20Monday%20after%20blaming%20the%20all-you-can-eat%20crustacean%20deal%20for%20its%20bankruptcy.%3Cp%3E4kodiak%2FGetty%20Images%2FiStockphoto%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERed%20Lobster%20once%20blamed%20its%20blockbuster%20Endless%20Shrimp%20deal%20for%20its%20downfall.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20the%20all-you-can-eat%20promo%20is%20back%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20vibe%20is%20different.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20customers%20worry%20the%20value%20isn't%20the%20same%2C%20and%20the%20deal%20isn't%20driving%20the%20traffic%20it%20once%20did.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEndless%20Shrimp%20is%20back%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20not%20exactly%20causing%20a%20stampede.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20recent%20evening%20at%20a%20Red%20Lobster%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20diners%20ordered%20the%20all-you-can-eat%20deal%2C%20and%20the%20restaurant%20was%20busier%20than%20usual.%20However%2C%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20dining%20room%20sat%20empty%2C%20and%20the%20pace%20never%20tipped%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-red-lobster-staff-nightmare-endless-shrimp-returns-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echaos%20that%20servers%20remember%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20past%20runs%20of%20the%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20popular%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20server%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20not%20as%20popular%20as%20I%20would%20have%20thought.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20notable%20shift%20for%20a%20deal%20that%20once%20defined%20the%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20overwhelmed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERed%20Lobster%20has%20brought%20back%20Endless%20Shrimp%20for%20a%20limited%20run%2C%20six%20weeks%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20servers%20said%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ereviving%20a%20promotion%20it%20once%20said%20it%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20keep.%20CEO%20Damola%20Adamolekun%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20year%20that%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20plans%26quot%3B%20to%20bring%20it%20back%2C%20after%20the%20company%20cited%20the%20deal%20as%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-endless-shrimp-bankruptcy-private-equity-debt-real-estate-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E2024%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20business%20could%20use%20a%20boost%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-bankruptcy-rebound-endless-shrimp-private-equity-adamolekun-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERed%20Lobster%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20it's%20reviving%20Endless%20Shrimp%20in%20response%20to%20customer%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20data%20suggests%20a%20more%20muted%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223740%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20various%20Endless%20Shrimp%20variations%20on%20a%20diner's%20table%20at%20Red%20Lobster%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ebedab367066d7c2970e8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222699%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEvery%20table%20in%20the%20occupied%20sections%20of%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20Red%20Lobster%20had%20a%20menu%20display%20promoting%20the%20return%20of%20Endless%20Shrimp.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFoot-traffic%20data%20from%20Advan%20shows%20Red%20Lobster%20saw%20a%20clear%20surge%20in%20visits%20during%20a%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-of-endless-shrimp-red-lobster-revives-deal-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEndless%20Shrimp%3C%2Fa%3E%20push%2C%20when%20it%20first%20made%20the%20promotion%20a%20permanent%20menu%20fixture.%20That%20bump%20wasn't%20seen%20in%202024%20or%202025%2C%20after%20it%20was%20removed%20from%20menus%2C%20and%20hasn't%20been%20as%20significant%20this%20time%20around.%20Advan's%20data%20shows%20that%20foot%20traffic%20the%20week%20of%20the%20latest%20Endless%20Shrimp%20launch%20was%20down%200.9%25%2C%20well%20below%20the%20prior%20surge%20and%20a%20dip%20compared%20to%20positive%20trends%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20traffic%20has%20been%20uneven%2C%20according%20to%20analysis%20by%20Placer.ai.%20After%20seeing%20a%20five-month%20surge%20last%20summer%2C%20when%20Adamolekun%20launched%20the%20chain's%20viral%20seafood%20boils%2C%20visits%20have%20been%20down%20year%20over%20year%20since%20November%202025.%20Placer%20did%20not%20have%20data%20available%20regarding%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20Endless%20Shrimp%20relaunch%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain's%202026%20performance%20has%20been%20affected%20by%20%26quot%3Bunfavorable%20weather%2C%20rising%20gas%20prices%2C%20and%20broader%20macroeconomic%20concerns%2C%26quot%3B%20Placer's%20head%20of%20analytical%20research%2C%20R.J.%20Hottovy%2C%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20shrimp%20promotion%20%26quot%3Bshould%20resonate%20with%20value-conscious%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it's%20arriving%20in%20a%20softer%2C%20less%20predictable%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECasual%20dining%20chains%20like%20Red%20Lobster%20are%20trying%20to%20win%20back%20customers%20in%20a%20tougher%20environment%20than%20they%20faced%20a%20decade%20ago.%20The%20industry%20is%20navigating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-k-shaped-economy-breaking-fast-food-playbook-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EK-shaped%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20higher-income%20diners%20are%20still%20spending%2C%20but%20middle-%20and%20lower-income%20consumers%20%E2%80%94%20long%20the%20backbone%20of%20chains%20like%20Red%20Lobster%20%E2%80%94%20are%20pulling%20back%20or%20trading%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20put%20pressure%20on%20legacy%20brands%20with%20higher%20price%20points%2C%20especially%20as%20competitors%20like%20Chili's%20lean%20into%20value%20deals%20and%20aggressively%20market%20cheaper%20options.%20For%20Red%20Lobster%2C%20which%20typically%20charges%20more%20than%20many%20casual-dining%20peers%2C%20that%20dynamic%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20convince%20diners%20they're%20getting%20a%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20even%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Bendless%26quot%3B%20one%20on%20the%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20former%20Red%20Lobster%20executives%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Endless%20Shrimp%20worked%20best%20as%20a%20tightly%20controlled%2C%20seasonal%20promotion%20%E2%80%94%20something%20rare%20enough%20to%20feel%20like%20an%20event%20and%20strategically%20timed%20to%20fill%20slower%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20they%20said%2C%20the%20company%20leaned%20on%20it%20more%20heavily%20to%20drive%20traffic%2C%20eroding%20the%20sense%20of%20urgency%20that%20once%20made%20it%20so%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20lost%20its%20appeal%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20executive%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20shift%20shows%20up%20not%20just%20in%20the%20data%2C%20but%20in%20the%20dining%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20customers%20are%20showing%20up%20for%20Endless%20Shrimp.%20One%20Los%20Angeles%20diner%2C%20Jeffrey%20Turney%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20visits%20Red%20Lobster%20every%20couple%20of%20months%20when%20promotions%20are%20running%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bexcited%20for%20the%20return%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20bottomless%20deal%2C%20enthusiastically%20texting%20friends%20about%20it%20as%20he%20waited%20for%20his%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20overall%20the%20meal%20was%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20he%20%26quot%3Breally%20disliked%26quot%3B%20the%20new%20Marry%20Me%20Shrimp%2C%20a%20social-media-driven%20flavor%20launched%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223495%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20plates%20of%20Endless%20Shrimp%20options%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Red%20Lobster%20diner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ebefb2367066d7c2970ea1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222929%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERed%20Lobster's%20Endless%20Shrimp%20menu%20features%20five%20variations%20of%20shrimp%20dishes%2C%20including%20coconut%20shrimp%20and%20linguini%20Alfredo.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20third%20of%20the%20diners%20at%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20location%20had%20purchased%20the%20deal%20during%20a%20recent%20dinner%20service%2C%20a%20server%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20skipped%20the%20bottomless%20shrimp%2C%20with%20some%20opting%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20different%20deals%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20%2430%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobsters-new-lobsterfest-menu-review-photos-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esteak%20and%20lobster%3C%2Fa%3E%20Wednesday%20night%20special%2C%20which%20carries%20the%20same%20price%20tag%20as%20the%20Endless%20Shrimp%20promotion%20in%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20that%20they%20brought%20it%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Destiny%20Howard%2C%20a%20social%20media%20creator%20and%20Red%20Lobster%20fan%20who%20runs%20the%20account%20%26quot%3BMunch%20with%20Des%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20move%20shows%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Blistening%20to%20their%20customers.%26quot%3B%20She%20framed%20the%20appeal%20in%20terms%20of%20responsiveness%20and%20novelty%2C%20not%20necessarily%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20diners%2C%20the%20math%20doesn't%20add%20up.%20With%20restaurants%20charging%20between%20%2424.99%20and%20%2429.99%20for%20unlimited%20servings%20of%20five%20dishes%2C%20depending%20on%20location%2C%20some%20felt%20it%20wasn't%20a%20particularly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobsters-all-you-can-eat-endless-shrimp-backfires-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egood%20bargain%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20compared%20with%20other%20menu%20options%20at%20the%20same%20price%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20too%20happy%20with%20the%20raise%20in%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Turney%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20%2430%2C%20I%20think%20you%20should%20get%20at%20least%20two%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20but%20noted%20that%20groceries%20and%20dining%20out%20have%20gotten%20more%20expensive%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20perception%20lines%20up%20with%20broader%20industry%20pressures%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-seafood-boil-review-photos-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeafood%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20risen%2C%20and%20casual%20dining%20chains%20are%20increasingly%20competing%20on%20value%20with%20both%20fast-food%20and%20fast-casual%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEndless%20Shrimp%20was%20never%20just%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-red-lobster-endless-shrimp-bankruptcy-filing-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echeap%20seafood%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20about%20drawing%20people%20in%20during%20slow%20months%2C%20ideally%20to%20order%20something%20with%20a%20higher%20margin%2C%20the%20former%20executives%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20while%20the%20promotion%20is%20bringing%20some%20diners%20through%20the%20door%2C%20it's%20not%20clear%20whether%20it's%20delivering%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20lift.%20For%20Red%20Lobster%2C%20that%20may%20be%20beside%20the%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20is%20running%20Endless%20Shrimp%20at%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20its%20fiscal%20year%20and%20during%20a%20typically%20slower%20stretch%2C%20a%20window%20when%20a%20modest%20bump%20in%20traffic%20can%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20former%20executive%20put%20it%2C%20the%20promotion%20can%20still%20work%20as%20a%20lever%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrive%20business%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20if%20it%20no%20longer%20carries%20the%20same%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20customers%20like%20Turney%2C%20the%20comeback%20doesn't%20quite%20hit%20as%20it%20used%20to.%C2%A0He%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20back%20again%20for%20Endless%20Shrimp%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he'd%20be%20willing%20to%20give%20something%20else%20a%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-endless-shrimp-returns-but-hype-faded-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777435262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f166483b4f7c3af2b7ae7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-lobster-endless-shrimp-returns-but-hype-faded-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Red%20Lobster%20once%20blamed%20its%20blockbuster%20Endless%20Shrimp%20deal%20for%20its%20downfall.%20Now%20the%20all-you-can-eat%20promo%20is%20back%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20vibe%20is%20different.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20worked%20in%20startups%20across%20China%20and%20the%20US%20for%2020%20years.%20The%20American%20playbook%20is%20easier%20to%20follow.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chalres%20Yang%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8209f3fecbb42897a275d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharles%20Yang%20has%20only%20worked%20in%20startups%20in%20China%20and%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3ECharles%20Yang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECharles%20Yang%20spent%2010%20years%20building%20a%20startup%20in%20China%20before%20moving%20to%20the%20US%20to%20start%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20that%20China's%20startup%20scene%20feels%20less%20structured%20than%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20China%2C%20government%20direction%2C%20cultural%20norms%2C%20and%20community-first%20values%20shape%20how%20startups%20are%20built.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Charles%20Yang%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Vibe%2C%20a%20US-based%20AI%20workspace%20startup.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20first%20company%20with%20my%20friend%20after%20finishing%20my%20third%20year%20at%20Zhejiang%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20remember%20the%20morning%20in%20January%202006.%20We%20went%20to%20the%20bank%2C%20and%20my%20father%20gave%20me%20about%20%245%2C000.%20My%20friends%20and%20I%20used%20that%20sum%20to%20start%20our%20own%20gaming%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freason-incoming-freshman-wants-computer-science-degree-despite-ai-fears-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecomputer%20science%20major%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%20conventional%20pathways%20laid%20out%3A%20You%20can%20go%20to%20big%20companies%20like%20Microsoft%2C%20Baidu%2C%20or%20Alibaba%3B%20pursue%20a%20master's%20degree%2C%20then%20a%20Ph.D%2C%20or%20go%20to%20the%20US%20to%20study%20for%20a%20Ph.D%20and%20stay%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdropped-out-of-college-ai-founder-sacrifice-trade-off-cancer-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equit%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20three%20years%20to%20build%20my%20startup.%20My%20family%20did%20care%20about%20whether%20I%20would%20graduate%2C%20because%20I%20was%20the%20only%20one%20in%20my%20family%20who%20attended%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20so%20young%20that%20I%20do%20not%20think%20there%20was%20any%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3Brisk%26quot%3B%20in%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274426676-13cf-4d8b-98c2-eabaaedf2d15%5C%22%3EMoving%20to%20the%20US%20for%20a%20global%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%2010%20years%2C%20my%20gaming%20company%20became%20very%20successful.%20We%20considered%20selling%20or%20going%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20married%20and%20had%20a%20daughter%2C%20so%20I%20began%20thinking%20about%20my%20next%20career%20and%20life%20goal.%20If%20you%20go%20public%2C%20you're%20tied%20to%20the%20company%20for%20at%20least%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20a%20better%20answer%20if%20my%20kid%20asked%20what%20I%20do.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20build%20another%20Chinese%20game.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20big%20global%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Seattle%2C%20met%20friends%20at%20Apple%20and%20Google%2C%20and%20saw%20Silicon%20Valley.%20I%20had%20spent%2011%20years%20building%20virtual%20things%2C%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20new%20startup%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhardware-tech-spotlight-wall-street-bet-google-apple-data-centers-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esomething%20real%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stepped%20away%20from%20my%20gaming%20company%20in%20China.%20I%20built%20an%20early-stage%20immersive%20collaboration%20platform%20exploring%20spatial%20computing%20for%20teamwork%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20raised%20%241%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20advantages%20in%20linking%20China's%20supply%20chain%20to%20the%20US%20ecosystem.%20We've%20managed%20to%20build%20products%20and%20scale%20the%20business%20through%20e-commerce%2C%20and%20set%20up%20distribution%20and%20sales%20pipelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20I%20pivoted%20my%20startup%20to%20the%20AI%20workspace%2C%20and%20we%20are%20backed%20by%20Sequoia%20Capital%20China%2C%20now%20known%20as%20HongShan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b9b47fb-ae4c-4683-89dd-fab2de6f9ead%5C%22%3EIn%20China%2C%20startups%20feel%20unstructured.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20they%20run%20off%20a%20playbook%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20startup%20environment%20feels%20like%20a%20well-documented%20software%20development%20kit.%20You%20follow%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-is-the-startup-playbook-follow-when-money-is-tight-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20the%20playbook%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20even%20some%20wildcards%20are%20documented%20in%20a%20systematic%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20China%2C%20the%20startup%20environment%20is%20more%20like%20a%20badly%20documented%20system.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20bugs%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20holes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20society%20follows%20blurred%2C%20vague%2C%20and%20hidden%20rules.%20Usually%20in%20China%2C%20relationships%20are%20built%20through%20dinners%20and%20drinking%20wine%20with%20people.%20A%20lot%20of%20opportunities%20come%20from%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-culture-stability-success-startup-founder-kuse-yuhao-xu-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIn%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20don't%20put%20yourself%20first.%20You%20are%20part%20of%20the%20community%20first%2C%20then%20yourself.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20it%20is%20more%20individualistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pre-pandemic%20period%20was%20probably%20the%20golden%20age%20for%20many%20Chinese%20tech%20startups%2C%20where%20many%20young%20people%20chose%20to%20start%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20in%20China%2C%20resources%20are%20being%20allocated%20more%20to%20state-owned%20organizations%20and%20startups%20that%20prefer%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-openclaw-craze-live-decade-west-learn-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egovernment-led%20direction%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20Beijing%20wants%20something%2C%20then%20a%20lot%20of%20resources%20go%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20it%20is%20more%20organic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22632a4459-e02d-4631-bb35-315b71b1390b%5C%22%3EAdvice%20to%20startup%20founders%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20someone%20more%20independent%20or%20ambitious%2C%20I%20would%20probably%20suggest%20they%20join%20a%20successful%20company%20for%20at%20least%20two%20or%20three%20years.%20I%20think%20I%20missed%20out%20on%20that%20at%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20when%20to%20build%20a%20company%20for%20yourself%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20strong%20interest%20in%20something%2C%20just%20do%20it.%20Being%20young%20and%20not%20having%20experience%20does%20not%20necessarily%20prevent%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it%20is%20really%20about%20your%20passion%20%E2%80%94%20and%20having%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20a%20tech%20career%20in%20China%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acmlee%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ecmlee%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-life-china-us-10-years-charles-yang-tech-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777435261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8209f3fecbb42897a275d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-life-china-us-10-years-charles-yang-tech-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Charles%20Yang%20spent%2010%20years%20building%20startups%20in%20