ement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Want%20to%20hire%20for%20your%20robotics%20startup%3F%20The%20autonomous%20vehicle%20industry%20is%20ripe%20for%20picking.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222943%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Panelists%20on%20stage%20at%20a%20Physical%20AI%20Industry%20night.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1495129fef86fd43d3cd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222207%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThree%20of%20the%20four%20panelists%20at%20a%20%26quot%3BPhysical%20AI%20Industry%20Night%26quot%3B%20are%20autonomous-vehicle%20alums%20now%20working%20in%20robotics.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Foxglove%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20autonomous%20vehicle%20industry%20is%20hyper-focused%20on%20scaling%20self-driving%20cars%20in%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStartup%20CEOs%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20experience%20transfers%20well%20to%20the%20broader%20robotics%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAV%20engineers%20have%20seen%20the%20full%20development%20cycle%20from%20data%20collection%20to%20deployment%2C%20CEOs%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20robotics%20world%20races%20to%20mature%20beyond%20closed%20demonstrations%2C%20founders%20and%20CEOs%20in%20the%20robotics%20space%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20experience%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxi-autonomous-vehicle-industry-maturity-hype-conference-ride-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeploying%20self-driving%20cars%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20real%20world%20makes%20AV%20employees%20ideal%20candidates%20for%20hire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20definitely%20look%20for%20AV%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Adrian%20Macneil%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Foxglove%2C%20a%20data%20infrastructure%20platform%20for%20robotics%20companies%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20is%20that%20AV%20was%20the%20first%20big%20application%20of%20physical%20AI%2C%20so%20people%20who%20have%20worked%20at%20AV%20companies%20have%20seen%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20ship%20complex%20physical%20AI%20at%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacneil%20himself%20was%20an%20alum%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxis-general-motors-cruise-problems-tesla-elon-musk-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Motors'%20robotaxi%20venture%2C%20Cruise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20before%20founding%20his%20startup%20in%202021.%20At%20his%20startup%2C%20which%20has%2075%20employees%2C%20roughly%2040%25%20are%20from%20AV%20or%20AV-adjacent%20companies%2C%20he%20said%2C%20including%20Waymo%2C%20Motional%2C%20Aurora%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapplied-intuition-marc-andreessen-challenges-of-real-world-physical-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApplied%20Intuition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Luminar%2C%20and%20Cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutonomous%20vehicles%20are%20a%20marriage%20of%20software%20and%20hardware%2C%20roughly%20boiled%20down%20to%20turning%20noisy%20real-world%20data%20into%20safe%20and%20reliable%20physical%20action%2C%20i.e.%2C%20steering%20a%20car.%20Zoom%20in%20further%2C%20and%20the%20cycle%20could%20entail%20data%20collection%2C%20training%20the%20driving%20models%2C%20validating%20safety%2C%20and%2C%20finally%2C%20deploying%20autonomous%20cars.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FKcq0tjmvGOs%3Fsi%3DTOUvc-3h9TyxNkXp%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERobots%2C%20whether%20utilized%20for%20home%20or%20industrial%20applications%2C%20will%20require%20a%20similar%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETony%20Zhao%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsunday-robotics-home-robot-training-hands-loading-dishwasher-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESunday%20Robotics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20building%20home%20robots%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20seeing%20AV%20experience%20on%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20is%20a%20plus.%20He%20sees%20talent%20transfer%20on%20both%20the%20software%20and%20hardware%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20hardware%2C%20there%20are%20just%20not%20that%20many%20exciting%20hardware%20companies%20that%20combine%20AI%20and%20cutting-edge%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20software%20perspective%2C%20Zhao%20said%20the%20pipeline%20from%20data%20input%20to%20driving%20output%20requires%20what's%20called%20%26quot%3Bsystems-level%20thinking%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20engineers%20must%20ask%20questions%20such%20as%20which%20sensors%20are%20most%20appropriate%20or%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxi-human-labor-industry-data-labelers-annotators-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emessy%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20translate%20into%20real-world%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20different%20from%20working%20with%20Large%20Language%20Models%2C%20where%20the%20input%20and%20output%20are%20all%20text%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20straightforward%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20cofounder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20company%20of%20about%2070%20people%2C%20Zhao%20said%20between%2030%25%20to%2050%25%20of%20his%20startup%20have%20AV-related%20backgrounds%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-loses-ai-staff-startup-sunday-robotics-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexperience%20at%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Zhao%20and%20his%20cofounder%2C%20Cheng%20Chi%2C%20are%20also%20AV%20alums%3A%20Zhao%20worked%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fashok-elluswamy-tesla-autopilot-elon-musk-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla's%20Autopilot%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Chi%20was%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Nuro%2C%20which%20is%20now%20preparing%20for%20a%20commercial%20launch%20of%20robotaxis%20with%20Uber%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be58b971-76ab-48a2-9333-4529e71544ed%5C%22%3E'A%20very%20small%20community'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20Thursday%20night%20in%20San%20Francisco's%20South%20of%20Market%20neighborhood%2C%20Macneil's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFoxglove%20and%20VC%20firm%20Eclipse%20Capital%20turned%20a%20nightclub%20into%20a%20gathering%20space%20for%20its%20first%20%26quot%3BPhysical%20AI%20Industry%20Night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20crowd%20of%20people%20inside%20a%20venue.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f14aab9244129ecb2f91a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMore%20than%20200%20people%20from%20over%20110%20robotics%20companies%20attended%20a%20%26quot%3BPhysical%20AI%20Industry%26quot%3B%20night.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20out%20of%20the%20four%20speakers%20for%20the%20evening's%20panel%20were%20robotics%20executives%20who%20graduated%20from%20the%20AV%20industry%3A%20Kevin%20Peterson%2C%20CTO%20of%20Bedrock%20Robotics%2C%20who%20came%20from%20Waymo%3B%20Ruijie%20(RJ)%20He%2C%20founding%20technical%20member%20of%20Mind%20Robotics%2C%20who%20was%20a%20director%20at%20Zoox%3B%20and%20Behrad%20Toghi%2C%20AI%20%26amp%3B%20Robotics%20lead%20at%20General%20Motors%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-is-shutting-down-its-ev-project-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple's%20Special%20Projects%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%20working%20on%20autonomous%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20the%20ex-AV%20panelists%20spoke%20on%20the%20transferability%20of%20autonomous%20vehicle%20experience%20to%20robotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20best%20people%20to%20hire%20today%20to%20work%20on%20robotics%20are%20AV%20people%2C%20because%20it's%20very%20similar%2C%26quot%3B%20Toghi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20robotics%20field%20is%20starting%20to%20mirror%20some%20of%20the%20trends%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frideai-autonomous-vehicle-conference-review-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ematurity%20curve%20AVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20through%20from%202014%20to%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToghi%20said%20folks%20in%20the%20AV%20space%20also%20have%20experience%20working%20in%20large%20teams%20because%20evaluating%20and%20validating%20autonomous%20vehicle%20technology%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20operation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ruijie%20He%20of%20Mind%20Robotics%20surrounded%20by%20younger%20startup%20founders%20and%20employees.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f14a369244129ecb2f91a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStartup%20founders%20and%20employees%20jockeyed%20for%20time%20to%20talk%20to%20Ruijie%20(RJ)%20He%20of%20Mind%20Robotics.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERitika%20Shrivastava%2C%20who%20was%20a%20Tesla%20Autopilot%20engineer%20before%20cofounding%20Ember%20Robotics%20in%202024%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20AV%20engineers%20have%20recognized%20the%20challenges%20that%20robotics%20now%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mindset%20is%20exactly%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20AVs%2C%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20planning%2C%20sensing%2C%20and%20actuation%2C%20and%20then%20you%20have%20the%20same%20exact%20thing%20in%20robotics%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20200%20people%20from%20over%20110%20robotics%20companies%20attended%20Thursday's%20Physical%20AI%20night%2C%20a%20Foxglove%20rep%20said.%20And%20nearly%2030%20of%20those%20companies%20came%20from%20the%20mobility%20sector%2C%20including%20Waymo%2C%20Tesla%2C%20Zoox%2C%20Nissan%2C%20and%20Toyota%20Research%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20employees%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20for%20this%20story%20said%20they%20were%20merely%20curious%20attendees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhao%20didn't%20attend%20the%20Physical%20AI%20night%2C%20but%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20was%20familiar%20with%20a%20few%20of%20the%20speakers%20and%20companies%2C%20including%20Pete%20Florence%2C%20CEO%20of%20Generalist%20robotics%2C%20who%20was%20another%20panelist.%20Zhao%20recalled%20being%20in%20the%20same%20room%20with%20Florence%20and%20others%20around%202023%20when%20they%20were%20at%20Google%20DeepMind%20before%20they%20moved%20on%20to%20start%20a%20robotics%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20small%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautonomous-vehiecle-industry-humanoid-robots-startups-hiring-talent-pool-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777425776000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1495129fef86fd43d3cd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautonomous-vehiecle-industry-humanoid-robots-startups-hiring-talent-pool-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Veterans%20of%20the%20autonomous%20vehicle%20industry%20who%20founded%20their%20own%20robotics%20outfit%20told%20BI%20that%20AV%20experience%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20transferable%20skills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3