%20kicked%20off%20Tuesday%20and%20Musk%20was%20the%20first%20witness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20compared%20AI%20to%20a%20very%20smart%20child%20that%20needs%20someone%20to%20%26quot%3Binstill%20the%20right%20values%26quot%3B%20in%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20cited%20meetings%20with%20Larry%20Page%20and%20Barack%20Obama%20as%20evidence%20of%20long-held%20concerns%20over%20AI%20safety.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20dropped%20some%20big%20names%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20he%20sought%20to%20convince%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-shows-up-court-jury-selection-elon-musk-trial-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ean%20Oakland%20federal%20jury%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20is%20serious%20about%20AI%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20nine-person%20jury%20that%20he%20had%20a%20one-on-one%20meeting%20with%20former%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20in%202015.%20Instead%20of%20asking%20for%20favors%20for%20his%20company%2C%20he%20%26quot%3Bspent%20an%20hour%26quot%3B%20warning%20Obama%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20AI%2C%20which%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20was%20really%20using%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%20testified%20that%20Larry%20Page%20called%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bspeciest%26quot%3B%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Bpro-humanity%26quot%3B%20over%20AI%20in%202015%2C%20when%20Page%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarry-page-elon-musk-specieist-ai-dangers-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20it%20was%20extremely%20important%20to%20have%20a%20counterbalance%20to%20Google%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20about%20cofounding%20OpenAI%20at%20a%20time%20when%20he%20already%20had%20many%20other%20ventures%2C%20such%20as%20SpaceX%20and%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20did%20not%20seem%20to%20care%20about%20AI%20safety%20at%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20was%20the%20first%20witness%20in%20his%20civil%20trial%20against%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sam-altman-openai-trial-testimony-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20OpenAI%20and%20Sam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20high-stakes%20battle%20of%20the%20billionaires%20that%20could%20reshape%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20roughly%20two%20hours%20of%20testimony%2C%20Musk%20said%20he%20will%20always%20be%20%26quot%3Bpro-humans%26quot%3B%20should%20humans%20and%20AI%20come%20into%20conflict.%20He%20also%20testified%20about%20his%20early%20career%2C%20his%20lack%20of%20work-life%20balance%2C%20and%20his%20efforts%20to%20recruit%20AI%20researcher%20Ilya%20Sutskever%20from%20Google%20to%20work%20for%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLarry%20Page%20refused%20to%20speak%20to%20me%20ever%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20and%20Page's%20family%20office%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20lawsuit%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-elon-musk-and-sam-altman-relationship-feuds-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20and%20CEO%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeks%20more%20than%20%24100%20billion%20in%20damages%2C%20along%20with%20a%20request%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-vs-openai-sam-altman-legal-battle-stakes-microsoft-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunwind%20the%20for-profit%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20%24850%20billion%20company%20behind%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20case%20is%20Musk's%20accusation%20that%20OpenAI's%20founders%2C%20including%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20abandoned%20their%20founding%20mission%20as%20a%20nonprofit%20dedicated%20to%20developing%20AI%20for%20the%20public's%20benefit%2C%20and%20not%20for%20private%20gain.%20The%20Tesla%20CEO%20claims%20that%20Altman%20and%20OpenAI%20president%20Greg%20Brockman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sues-sam-altman-betrays-openai-mission-chatgpt-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeceived%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20donating%20%2438%20million%20toward%20this%20mission%20when%20they%20cofounded%20the%20company%20together%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20court%20loss%20would%20be%20a%20blow%20to%20charitable%20giving%2C%20he%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20become%20precedent%2C%20and%20it%20will%20give%20license%20to%20looting%20every%20charity%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in%202024%2C%20says%20Altman%20and%20Brockman%20used%20his%20money%20to%20create%20a%20%26quot%3Bfor-profit%2C%20market-paralyzing%20gorgon%26quot%3B%20that%20effectively%20turned%20OpenAI%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bsubsidiary%20of%20Microsoft.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-completes-restructuring-for-profit-signs-new-microsoft-agreement-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20completed%20a%20major%20restructuring%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20shifted%20the%20company%20toward%20a%20more%20conventional%20for-profit%20structure%2C%20with%20Microsoft%20holding%20a%20roughly%2027%25%20ownership%20stake%20in%20the%20for-profit%20entity%2C%20which%20remains%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20nonprofit%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20Tuesday's%20testimony%2C%20Musk%20compared%20AI%20to%20a%20very%20smart%20child%2C%20saying%20it%20could%20%26quot%3Bblow%20up%26quot%3B%20and%20run%20out%20of%20control%20without%20someone%20to%20%26quot%3Binstill%20the%20right%20values%26quot%3B%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20has%20been%20my%20long-standing%20concern%20about%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20what%20happens%20when%20the%20computer%20gets%20much%20smarter%20than%20humans%3F%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Monday