3EStarbucks%20may%20be%20fueled%20by%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-coffee-menu-food-sale-review-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20company%20is%20increasingly%20catering%20to%20customers%20don't%20actually%20need%20coffee%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20people%20that%20weren't%20energy%20drinkers%20in%20the%20morning%20become%20energy%20drinkers%20in%20the%20morning%20with%20our%20Refresher%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20CFO%20Cathy%20Smith%20said%20during%20Tuesday's%20second-quarter%20earnings%20call%2C%20pointing%20to%20a%20shift%20in%20how%20customers%20get%20their%20caffeine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20launched%20its%20new%20Energy%20Refreshers%20platform%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20offering%20three%20new%20varieties%20of%20its%20fruit-flavored%20drinks%2C%20which%20are%20made%20by%20mixing%20concentrated%20juice-based%20blends%20with%20water%2C%20coconut%20milk%2C%20or%20lemonade.%20The%20Energy%20Refreshers%20line%20builds%20on%20Starbucks'%20existing%20classic%20Refreshers%2C%20launched%20in%202012%2C%20which%20contain%20lower%20caffeine%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Energy%20Refreshers%20have%20between%20100mg%20of%20caffeine%20in%20a%20small%20or%20%26quot%3Btall%26quot%3B%20serving%20and%20up%20to%20175mg%20in%20an%20extra%20large%20or%20%26quot%3Btrenta%26quot%3B%20serving.%20All%20Refreshers%20can%20now%20be%20made%20with%20customizable%20caffeine%20levels%2C%20including%20none%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20we%20added%20the%20customizable%20energy%2C%20we're%20seeing%20people%20take%20away%20the%20caffeine%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said%2C%20suggesting%20Starbucks%20is%20reshaping%20not%20only%20what%20people%20drink%2C%20but%20when%20and%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20shift%20is%20central%20to%20Starbucks'%20next%20phase%20of%20growth.%20The%20company%20has%20built%20what%20it%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3B%242%20billion%20platform%26quot%3B%20around%20its%20Refreshers%20as%20the%20broader%20beverage%20industry%20moves%20in%20the%20same%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20both%20fast-food%20brands%20and%20consumer%20packaged%20goods%20companies%20are%20racing%20to%20add%20ingredients%20such%20as%20fiber%2C%20protein%2C%20adaptogens%2C%20and%20nootropics%2C%20amid%20a%20%24200%20billion%20boom%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffunctional-drink-boom-wellness-arms-race-fiber-protein-adaptogens-nootropics-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efunctional%20drinks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20younger%20consumers%20are%20helping%20power%20beverage%20menu%20innovations%20across%20the%20industry%3A%20Gen%20Z's%20preference%20for%20unique%2C%20non-alcoholic%2C%20and%20highly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-driving-fast-food-beverage-wars-demand-custom-drinks-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecustomizable%20beverages%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20pushing%20chains%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20Starbucks%20and%20McDonald's%20%E2%80%94%20to%20compete%20on%20drinks%20that%20are%20as%20much%20about%20personalization%20and%20experience%20as%20they%20are%20about%20caffeine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20a%20Starbucks%20menu%20that's%20less%20about%20espresso%20and%20more%20about%20%26quot%3Bdrink%20experiences%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-office-near-brian-niccol-newport-beach-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBrian%20Niccol%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20during%20Tuesday's%20earnings%20call%2C%20whether%20that's%20a%20morning%20ritual%20or%20an%20afternoon%20pick-me-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20plans%20to%20keep%20pushing%20in%20that%20direction%2C%20with%20executives%20saying%20they'll%20continue%20to%20build%20on%20its%20Refresher%20platform%2C%20expand%20flavor%20options%2C%20and%20launch%20blended%20versions%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broader%20%26quot%3BBack%20to%20Starbucks%26quot%3B%20initiative%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20Niccol%2C%20is%20showing%20clear%20momentum%20as%20it%20leans%20into%20the%20new%20drink%20category.%20In%20its%20fiscal%20second%20quarter%2C%20Starbucks%20reported%20about%20%249.5%20billion%20in%20revenue%2C%20with%20US%20comparable%20sales%20up%207.1%25%20driven%20largely%20by%20higher%20transaction%20volumes%2C%20and%20posted%20its%20first%20year-over-year%20earnings%20growth%20in%20more%20than%202%20years.%20Its%20stock%20was%20up%20more%20than%205%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20results%20suggest%20Starbucks'%20strategy%20is%20working%2C%20while%20its%20growth%20is%20increasingly%20driven%20by%20products%20that%20look%20less%20like%20traditional%20coffee%2C%20including%20its%20expanded%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-protein-drinks-are-helping-fuel-gains-for-the-chain-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotein%20drink%20menu%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20Energy%20Refreshers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENiccol%20said%20competitors%20are%20already%20following%20Starbucks'%20lead%2C%20adding%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Balmost%20a%20compliment%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Refresher%20platform%20is%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20imitated%26quot%3B%20by%20other%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaco%20Bell%20launched%20its%20Rockstar%20Energy%20Refrescas%20nationwide%20in%20June%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3E%202025%2C%20and%20Panera%20this%20year%20launched%20its%20own%20line%20of%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fmark%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpanera-tries-again-caffeinated-drinks-far-less-caffeine-charged-lemonade-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3EEnergy%20Refreshers%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%20