ith%20costs%20remaining%20below%20%2430%20per%20active%20day%20for%2090%25%20of%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20Claud%20Code%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcode.claude.com%2Fdocs%2Fen%2Fcosts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereads%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BTo%20estimate%20spend%20for%20your%20own%20team%2C%20start%20with%20a%20small%20pilot%20group%20and%20use%20the%20tracking%20tools%20below%20to%20establish%20a%20baseline%20before%20wider%20rollout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArchived%20versions%20of%20the%20same%20page%20showed%20that%20before%20April%2016%2C%20the%20previous%20estimates%20were%20%246%20per%20developer%20per%20active%20day%20with%20costs%20remaining%20below%20%2412%20per%20active%20day%20%26quot%3Bfor%2090%25%20of%20users.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-cant-stop-talking-about-tokens-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETokens%20are%20how%20large%20language%20models%20break%20down%20words%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Einto%20numerical%20inputs%20and%20outputs%2C%20and%20are%20essentially%20the%20building%20blocks%20of%20AI%20chatbots%20like%20Anthropic's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEd%20Zitron%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20EZPR%2C%20a%20tech%20and%20business%20PR%20firm%2C%20first%20pointed%20out%20the%20change%20on%20X.%20Zitron%20was%20previously%20a%20columnist%20for%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20stealth-tweaked%20their%20claude%20code%20docs%20to%20increase%20the%20estimated%20average%20that%20a%20developer%20would%20spen