%20true%20moccasin%20construction%20and%20left%20unlined%20for%20lightness%2C%20these%20feel%20closer%20to%20a%20dress%20shoe%20than%20your%20average%20boat%20shoe.%20The%20quality%20is%20immediate%20the%20moment%20you%20put%20them%20on%2C%20soft%2C%20pliable%2C%20and%20incredibly%20comfortable%2C%20thanks%20to%20that%20supple%20Italian%20suede%20that%20molds%20to%20your%20foot%20over%20time.%20A%20tonal%20rubber%20sole%20adds%20grip%20without%20disrupting%20the%20clean%20look%2C%20and%20the%20sleek%20silhouette%20works%20just%20as%20well%20with%20linen%20trousers%2C%20a%20tropical%20wool%20suit%2C%20or%20dressier%20shorts.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20colorways%2Fleathers%2C%20but%20for%20our%20money%2C%20the%20black%20suede%20(or%20the%20pebble%20grain)%20is%20the%20chicest%2C%20standing%20out%20from%20the%20usual%20brown%20or%20navy%20and%20leaning%20into%20the%20elegance%20these%20boat%20shoes%20exude.%20Overall%2C%20this%20investment-level%20pair%20more%20than%20justifies%20the%20cost%2C%20blending%20classic%20American%20style%20with%20Italian%20craftsmanship%20that%20will%20last%20for%20years%20with%20proper%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20handmade%20heritage%3A%20Quoddy%20Runabout%20Boat%20Sole%20at%20Huckberry%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222730%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Quoddy%20boat%20shoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0c52729fef86fd43d3776%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222047%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Stefanov%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20know%20handmade%20heritage%2C%20you%20know%20Quoddy.%20I%20was%20first%20introduced%20to%20the%20brand%20by%20a%20colleague%20at%20Esquire%2C%20who%20pointed%20me%20toward%20the%20IYKYK%20moccasin%20makers%20as%20a%20true%20example%20of%20the%20finest%20American%20craftsmanship.%20Quoddy%20is%20one%20of%20those%20rare%20brands%20still%20doing%20things%20the%20old%20way%2C%20hand-sewn%20in%20Maine%20by%20artisans%20who've%20been%20perfecting%20the%20craft%20for%20decades.%20From%20the%20small-batch%20production%20to%20the%20true%20moccasin%20construction%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20leathers%20(which%20break%20in%20beautifully)%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20the%20intention%20behind%20every%20pair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20of%20course%2C%20the%20sharp%20eyes%20at%20Huckberry%20know%20all%20this%20too%2C%20as%20they%20recently%20released%20the%20Runabout%20boat%20shoe%2C%20an%20exclusive%20Quoddy%20model%20that%20carries%20all%20that%20DNA.%20You've%20got%20the%20classic%20two-eye%20design%20with%20fully%20functional%20360%20lacing%20for%20a%20secure%20cinch%2C%20embossed%20cushioned%20insoles%2C%20and%20a%20build%20that%20feels%20surprisingly%20lightweight%20and%20almost%20sneaker-like%20on%20foot.%20The%20rubber%20outsole%20is%20grippy%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20bounce%2C%20the%20cushioning%20is%20legit%2C%20and%20details%20like%20side%20ventilation%2C%20waxed%20cotton%20laces%2C%20and%20a%20reinforced%20heel%20mean%20these%20can%20log%20comfortable%20miles%2C%20from%20long%20walks%20on%20the%20dock%20to%20days%20out%20on%20the%20water.%20They%20take%20a%20minute%20to%20break%20in%2C%20but%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20appeal.%20These%20are%20for%20the%20guy%20who%20cares%20about%20craft%2C%20wants%20something%20that%20isn't%20mass%2C%20values%20durability%2C%20and%20appreciates%20a%20boat%20shoe%20that%20gets%20better%20every%20summer%20of%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20comfort%3A%20Sebago%20Docksides%20Portland%20Crazy%20H%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222621%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sebago%20boat%20shoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efccca367066d7c2971a6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221965%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Stefanov%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20did%20you%20really%20think%20we'd%20do%20a%20best%20boat%20shoe%20list%20without%20featuring%20the%20other%20OG%2C%20the%20Sebago%20Docksides%3F%20If%20Sperry%20is%20the%20origin%20story%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsebago-usa.com%2Fproducts%2Fdocksides-portland-crazy-h-forest-green%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDocksides%20Portland%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20equally%20respected%20continuation%2C%20with%20modern%20flourishes%20and%20that%20unmistakable%20maritime%20DNA%20baked%20in%20(more%20on%20that%20below).%20The%20name%20itself%20nods%20to%20Portland%2C%20one%20of%20New%20England's%20largest%20seaports%2C%20and%20these%20are%20built%20with%20heritage%20in%20mind%3A%20hand-sewn%20construction%2C%20authentic%20detailing%2C%20and%20that%20rugged%2C%20mold-to-your-foot-over-time%20feel%20that%20guys%20who%20spend%20time%20around%20the%20water%20appreciate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20box%2C%20I%20noticed%20how%20light%20yet%20substantial%20they%20feel%2C%20and%20how%20comfortable%20they%20are%20on%20foot.%20That%20comes%20down%20to%20the%20leather%20sock%20lining%20and%20a%20slightly%20padded%20footbed%20that%20almost%20had%20an%20orthopedic%20feel%20(clutch%20for%20long%20days%20on%20docks%20or%20just%20walking%20through%20maritime%20towns).%20You're%20also%20getting%20all%20the%20docksides%20details%3A%20a%20fully%20functional%20360%20rawhide%20lacing%20system%20and%20non-marking%2C%20anti-slip%20siped%20rubber%20soles%20that%20deliver%20grip%20in%20wet%20conditions.%20I%20wore%20them%20with%20and%20without%20socks%2C%20in%20the%20rain%2C%20and%20they%20performed%20well%20in%20both%20conditions%20with%20solid%20breathability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20classic%20variation%20is%20always%20a%20wise%20purchase%2C%20I%20dig%20that%20Sebago%20put%20a%20modern%20twist%20on%20these%20Docksides%20with%20what%20they%20call%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%26quot%3B%20leather%2C%20though%20to%20me%20it%20reads%20more%20like%20nubuck.%20Made%20from%20waxed%2C%20unlined%20pull-up%20leather%2C%20they%20develop%20a%20signature%20pattern%20of%20creases%2C%20marks%2C%20and%20lived-in%20character%20over%20time%2C%20making%20each%20pair%20feel%20uniquely%20yours.%20One%20note%3A%20they%20do%20run%20slightly%20large%2C%20so%20take%20a%20half%20size%20down%20for%20a%20perfect%20fit.%20All%20in%20all%2C%20plenty%20of%20boat%20shoes%20today%20skew%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20while%20the%20Docksides%20fit%20that%20lane%2C%20too%2C%20it%20stands%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20authentic%2C%20durable%2C%20and%20classic%20pairs%2C%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20suede%3A%20Sperry%20X%20J.%20Crew%20Authentic%20Original%20Two-Eye%20Boat%20Shoes%20in%20Roughout%20Suede%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222730%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22J.%20Crew%20x%20Sperry%20boat%20shoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efc77ba98bc8fdc096f6ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222047%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Stefanov%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20no%20boat%20shoes%20on%20this%20list%20speak%20to%20my%20personal%20style%20quite%20like%20these%2C%20with%20a%20heritage-coded%20cool%20that%20leans%20almost%20Britpop-esque.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126382319of-20%26h%3D22ea6df85ba732495a8a7ec848a2a7d3de2c0348dafb2eebee35ca99ab2e3fe9%26postID%3D69efa8c431845c865e338778%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fbest-boat-shoes-for-men%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.jcrew.com%252Fp%252Fmens%252Fcategories%252Fshoes%252Fboat-shoes%252Fsperryreg-x-jcrew%252520authentic-original-unisex-two-eye-boat-shoes-in-roughout-suede%252FCH137%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESperry%20x%20J.Crew%20Authentic%20Originals%3C%2Fa%3E%20hit%20that%20sweet%20spot%20of%20comfort%2C%20quality%2C%20and%20vintage%20style%2C%20pairing%20classic%20Sperry%20craftsmanship%20and%20detailing%20with%20a%20handsome%2C%20soft%20yet%20durable%20roughout%20suede%20from%20J.Crew.%20I've%20been%20wearing%20them%20around%20the%20apartment%2C%20where%20they%20almost%20feel%20like%20a%20slip-on%20(albeit%20with%20a%20legit%2C%20grippy%20rubber%20sole)%2C%20and%20then%20out%20for%20errands%20around%20Brooklyn.%20They%20have%20that%20easy%2C%20lived-in%20vibe%20right%20out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20with%20a%20style%20that's%20hard%20not%20to%20admire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20collaboration%20draws%20on%20vintage%20references%2C%20evident%20in%20the%20roughout%20suede%20uppers%2C%20the%20stitching%2C%20and%20the%20retro%20branding%20on%20the%20insole%20and%20heel%2C%20all%20of%20which%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20OG%202-Eye.%20While%20they%20still%20carry%20that%20Sperry%20DNA%2C%20like%20the%20rubber%20sole%20and%20functional%20360%20lacing%2C%20they%20lean%20more%20lifestyle%20crosser%20than%20a%20true%20on-the-boat%20pair.%20I'm%20not%20grabbing%20these%20for%20a%20full%20day%20on%20deck%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20point.%20They%20carry%20Sperry's%20credibility%20with%20J.Crew's%20universally%20appealing%20design%20touches%2C%20making%20for%20an%20exemplary%2C%20easygoing%20everyday%20pair.%20Retro-leaning%2C%20comfortable%2C%20and%20effortlessly%20cool%2C%20this%20is%20a%20pair%20I'll%20be%20wearing%20all%20summer%20long%20for%20record%20shopping%2C%20coffee%20hangs%2C%20and%20lounging%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20boat%20shoes%3Cp%3EEach%20pair%20featured%20here%20excels%20in%20its%20own%20lane%20and%20was%20evaluated%20accordingly.%20I%20wore%20every%20pair%20for%20several%20days%2C%20paying%20attention%20to%20comfort%2C%20traction%2C%20materials%2C%20construction%2C%20and%20overall%20feel.%20Some%20were%20worn%20with%20jeans%20or%20chinos%20around%20Brooklyn%2C%20others%20with%20shorts%20on%20warmer%20weekend%20boardwalks%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20many%20on%20rainy%2C%20slick%20surfaces%20or%20light%20trails%20when%20possible.%20I%20also%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20details%20that%20define%20the%20category%2C%20things%20like%20lacing%2C%20moccasin-style%20construction%2C%20how%20the%20leather%20or%20suede%20feels%2C%20and%20how%20the%20sole%20grips.%20With%20years%20spent%20covering%20style%20and%20trust%20in%20the%20brands%20here%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20stand%20behind%20every%20pair%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20boat%20shoes%20above%20deliver%20on%20comfort%20and%20versatility%20while%20staying%20true%20to%20what%20defines%20the%20category.%20The%20difference%20comes%20down%20to%20how%20they%20fit%20into%20your%20day-to-day.%20Some%20are%20built%20for%20the%20deck%2C%20with%20functional%20360%20lacing%20and%20serious%20grip%2C%20while%20others%20lean%20more%20into%20everyday%20wear%2C%20made%20for%20casual%20weekends%2C%20travel%20days%2C%20and%20everything%20in%20between.%20Maybe%20it's%20a%20rugged%2C%20heritage%20leather%20pair%20that%20breaks%20in%20over%20time%2C%20a%20soft%20suede%20option%20with%20a%20more%20relaxed%20feel%2C%20a%20lug-sole%20version%20for%20extra%20traction%2C%20or%20a%20more%20polished%20take%20you%20can%20wear%20with%20tailoring.%20Boat%20shoes%20seem%20fairly%20straightforward%2C%20but%20there's%20nuance%20in%20how%20each%20wears%20and%20fits%20into%20your%20rotation.%20Every%20pair%20here%20delivers%20on%20quality%20and%20that%20core%20DNA%3B%20the%20difference%20is%20how%20it%20shows%20up%20in%20your%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20boat%20shoes%20for%20men%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20great%20menswear%20staples%2C%20boat%20shoes%20were%20born%20of%20function%3A%20Paul%20Sperry%20noticed%20his%20dog%20could%20grip%20icy%20ground%20better%20than%20he%20could%20and%20set%20out%20to%20recreate%20that%20traction%20for%20slick%20boat%20decks%2C%20ultimately%20developing%20the%20siped%20rubber%20sole%20that%20still%20defines%20the%20category%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20practical%20solution%20evolved%20into%20a%20style%20icon%2C%20with%20that%20enduring%20image%20of%20JFK%20in%20boat%20shoes%20becoming%20an%20American%20style%20reference%20for%20generations%20(and%20my%20personal%20favorite).%20They%20appear%20in%20cultural%20touchstones%20like%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Official%20Preppy%20Handbook%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20homage%20to%20the%20East%20Coast%20summer%20uniform%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3ETake%20Ivy%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20cult-classic%20photo%20book%20of%20Ivy%20League%20style.%20Boat%20shoes%20have%20been%20worn%20by%20Paul%20Newman%2C%20Ryan%20Reynolds%2C%20and%20Andrew%20Garfield%2C%20along%20with%20countless%20others.%20What%20began%20as%20a%20functional%20deck%20shoe%20is%20now%20a%20stylish%20standard.%20Aside%20from%20an%20iconic%20style%2C%20here's%20what%20you%20should%20look%20for%20in%20boat%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%20and%20Build%20Quality%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20is%20where%20a%20great%20boat%20shoe%20separates%20itself%20from%20the%20pair%20you%20regret%20by%20August.%20Traditional%20pairs%20are%20typically%20built%20from%20full-grain%20or%20pull-up%20leather%2C%20which%20is%20durable%2C%20molds%20to%20your%20foot%20over%20time%2C%20and%20develops%20that%20worn-in%20patina%20that%20only%20gets%20better%20with%20age.%20If%20you%20want%20something%20softer%20out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20suede%20or%20nubuck%20offers%20a%20more%20relaxed%2C%20broken-in%20feel%20while%20still%20holding%20up%20well%20for%20everyday%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20upper%2C%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20construction%20details.%20Hand-sewn%20stitching%2C%20a%20reinforced%20heel%2C%20and%20rawhide%20laces%20are%20hallmarks%2C%20along%20with%20the%20360-degree%20lacing%20system%2C%20which%20runs%20through%20the%20collar%20and%20can%20be%20tightened%20all%20the%20way%20around%20for%20a%20more%20secure%2C%20adjustable%20fit.%20That%20said%2C%20some%20opt%20for%20a%20non-functional%20360%20setup%20for%20a%20more%20streamlined%202-eye%20lace-up%2C%20which%20is%20generally%20fine%20for%20everyday%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20don't%20overlook%20the%20sole.%20A%20proper%20boat%20shoe%20should%20have%20a%20non-marking%20rubber%20outsole%20(often%20with%20siping%2C%20those%20razor-thin%20grooves%20that%20help%20channel%20water%20and%20improve%20grip%20on%20slick%20surfaces)%2C%20whether%20you're%20on%20a%20boat%20or%20navigating%20wet%20city%20sidewalks%20or%20a%20rain-soaked%20boardwalk.%20Either%20way%2C%20you%20want%20something%20that%20won't%20have%20you%20slipping%20when%20conditions%20get%20slick.%20That%20grippy%20rubber%20sole%20is%20one%20of%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20the%20category%2C%20even%20as%20some%20modern%20takes%2C%20like%20the%20Clarks%20or%20Timberland%20above%2C%20prioritize%20comfort%20or%20traction%20over%20a%20traditional%20deck-ready%20grip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%20and%20Comfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20good%20boat%20shoe%20should%20feel%20easy%20right%20out%20of%20the%20box%20and%20get%20better%20with%20wear.%20They%20might%20fit%20ever%20so%20slightly%20snug%20at%20first%2C%20especially%20if%20they're%20leather%2C%20but%20they'll%20stretch%20and%20mold%20to%20your%20foot%20over%20time.%20Most%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20worn%20with%20or%20without%20socks%2C%20so%20comfort%20and%20breathability%20are%20key.%20Look%20for%20leather-lined%20interiors%2C%20cushioned%20footbeds%2C%20or%20some%20level%20of%20arch%20support%2C%20which%20you'll%20appreciate%20by%20the%20end%20of%20a%20long%20day%20on%20your%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStyle%20and%20Texture%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20classic%20brown%20or%20navy%20leather%20pair%20will%20take%20you%20from%20shorts%20and%20a%20tee%20to%20lightweight%20chinos%20and%20a%20button-down%20with%20ease.%20Suede%20leans%20more%20textured%20and%20lifestyle-driven%2C%20while%20richer%20jewel%20tones%20or%20dark%20hues%20read%20more%20polished.%20Details%20like%20contrast%20stitching%20and%20sole%20profile%20subtly%20shift%20the%20vibe%2C%20whether%20that's%20more%20heritage-leaning%2C%20dressier%2C%20or%20lifestyle.%20Trust%20your%20eye%20here%20to%20complement%20your%20personal%20style%20and%20the%20occasions%20you%20plan%20to%20wear%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-boat-shoes-for-men%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777412422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f11d123b4f7c3af2b7ad5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-boat-shoes-for-men%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20men's%20boat%20shoes%20deliver%20comfort%2C%20grip%2C%20and%20timeless%20warm%20weather%20style%2C%20with%20options%20that%20look%20just%20as%20good%20on%20casually%20as%20they%20do%20on%20a%20boat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Stefanov)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Disney%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Toast%20to%20TV%E2%80%99%20Emmy%20FYC%20Kickoff%2C%20Hosted%20by%20Dana%20Walden%2C%20Celebrates%20With%20A-List%20Stars%2C%20Producers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777411854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236732588%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20a%20brief%20moment%20Monday%20night%2C%20Hollywood%20folks%20put%20aside%20any%20concerns%20they%20have%20about%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20troubles%20and%20found%20reason%20to%20celebrate%20at%20the%20Walt%20Disney%20Co.%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CToast%20to%20Television.%E2%80%9D%20The%20event%2C%20held%20at%20Soho%20House%20Hollywood%2C%20was%20exactly%20that%3A%20A%20moment%20for%20some%20of%20the%20medium%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20stars%2C%20creators%2C%20writers%2C%20executives%2C%20producers%20and%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Varietyschneider%22%2C