2C%20it%20can%20recharge%20using%20sunlight%20or%20indoor%20light%2C%20which%20remains%20a%20very%20cool%20feature.%20But%20I%20don't%20love%20the%20remote's%20overall%20design.%20It's%20not%20backlit%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20a%20bit%20cheap%20in%20hand%20compared%20to%20some%20other%20premium%20TV%20remotes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1f277b7-9364-4ef4-9eb6-2b70ef83b893%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20quality%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20S95H%20is%20the%20brightest%20OLED%20I've%20tested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Samsung%20S95H%20OLED%20TV%20mounted%20on%20a%20wall%20with%20an%20image%20of%20a%20cityscape%20at%20night%20on%20screen.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d6919dcc468aeec524d009%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20QD-OLED%20panel%20delivers%20an%20exceptional%20combination%20of%20high%20contrast%2C%20brightness%2C%20and%20color%20volume.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20testing%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126380930nb-20%26h%3D7c82c4412f31edef9f8b1698cbb3bb3e0f8863ae729c1303228560cc897ad3f2%26postID%3D69efbfea215b3a0a3c837e70%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsamsung-s95h-oled-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.samsung.com%252Fus%252Ftvs%252Foled-tv%252F65-inch-oled-4k-tv-s95h-sku-qn65s95hafxza%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES95H%3C%2Fa%3E%20wowed%20me%20with%20top-notch%20image%20quality.%20Like%20all%20OLED%20TVs%2C%20it%20delivers%20an%20infinite%20contrast%20ratio%2C%20allowing%20each%20pixel%20to%20dim%20and%20brighten%20independently.%20In%20a%20dark%20room%2C%20black%20levels%20completely%20disappear%2C%20producing%20the%20inky%20depth%20OLEDs%20are%20known%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViewing%20angl