0color%20space%20used%20in%20most%20modern%20Hollywood%20productions%20and%20about%2083%25%20of%20the%20wider%20BT.2020%20color%20space.%20That's%20not%20as%20high%20as%20Samsung's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-r95h-micro-rgb-tv-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ER95H%20Micro%20RGB%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20hit%2091%25%20of%20BT.2020%2C%20but%20it's%20an%20excellent%20number%20for%20an%20OLED.%20This%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20panel's%20quantum-dot%20technology%2C%20which%20helps%20the%20TV%20deliver%20a%20wider%2C%20brighter%20color%20range%20than%20a%20standard%20OLED.%20Though%20most%20current%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20don't%20require%20such%20high%20BT.2020%20coverage%2C%20that%20could%20change%20in%20the%20future%20as%20more%20filmmakers%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20gamut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColorful%2C%20bright%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BMad%20Max%3A%20Fury%20Road%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAquaman%26quot%3B%20looked%20fantastic%20on%20the%20S95H.%20Both%20films%20are%20great%20showcases%20for%20bold%20HDR%2C%20and%20the%20S95H%20delivered%20vibrant%2C%20impactful%20images%20with%20highlights%20that%20really%20popped%20from%20the%20screen.%20The%20TV's%20combination%20of%20high%20brightness%20and%20rich%20color%20gives%20these%20kinds%20of%20movies%20a%20level%20of%20intensity%20that%20midrange%20OLEDs%20can't%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222155%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Samsung%20S95H%20OLED%20TV%20hanging%20on%20a%20wall%20in%20a%20bright%20living%20room%20with%20a%20scene%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%26quot%3B%20on%20screen.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efc498a98bc8fdc096f6d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221616%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThough%20reflections%20are%20minimal%2C%20the%20screen%20does%20lift%20black%20levels%20a%20bit%20in%20bright%20rooms.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126380930nb-20%26h%3D7c82c4412f31edef9f8b1698cbb3bb3e0f8863ae729c1303228560cc897ad3f2%26postID%3D69efbfea215b3a0a3c837e70%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsamsung-s95h-oled-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.samsung.com%252Fus%252Ftvs%252Foled-tv%252F65-inch-oled-4k-tv-s95h-sku-qn65s95hafxza%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES95H%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20impressed%20me%20with%20darker%20material.%20The%20burning%20church%20scene%20in%20%26quot%3B1917%26quot%3B%20had%20excellent%20black%20levels%2C%20and%20the%20TV%20maintained%20good%20shadow%20detail.%20This%20is%20where%20OLED's%20pixel-level%20precision%20remains%20a%20big%20advantage%20over%20Mini%20LED%20models.%20Even%20the%20best%20Mini%20LED%20TVs%20need%20to%20rely%20on%20dimming%20zones%2C%20which%20can%20sometimes%20lead%20to%20blooming%20or%20uneven%20black%20levels.%20The%20S95H%20doesn't%20have%20that%20issue%20because%20it%20doesn't%20have%20a%20backlight.%20Dark%20areas%20remain%20even%20and%20precise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20those%20black%20levels%20do%20take%20a%20hit%20with%20the%20lights%20on%20because%20of%20the%20TV's%20anti-glare%20screen.%20When%20I%20watched%20the%20opening%20scene%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20bright%20room%2C%20black%20levels%20still%20looked%20decent%2C%20but%20they%20weren't%20as%20inky%20as%20they%20were%20in%20the%20dark.%20This%20is%20something%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%2C%20but%20it's%20likely%20an%20acceptable%20tradeoff%20for%20people%20who%20hate%20reflections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f54f171-9d47-43a3-9551-175fe4e79472%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20features%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESamsung's%20Tizen%20interface%20has%20been%20tweaked%20with%20a%20cleaner%20layout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222112%5C%