t-frame-tvs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFrame%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20still%20the%20brand's%20most%20decor-focused%20displays%2C%20but%20the%20S95H's%20design%20and%20Art%20Store%20access%20give%20it%20some%20of%20that%20same%20lifestyle%20appeal%20while%20delivering%20flagship%20OLED%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20Copilot%20AI%20is%20also%20integrated%2C%20bringing%20chatbot-like%20capabilities%20to%20the%20TV.%20It's%20a%20convenient%20extra%2C%20but%20not%20essential.%20While%20it's%20neat%20to%20ask%20your%20TV%20to%20help%20plan%20a%20vacation%20or%20answer%20detailed%20questions%2C%20I%20can%20do%20those%20things%20just%20as%20easily%20on%20my%20phone%20or%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECopilot%20was%20also%20a%20bit%20glitchy%20during%20my%20testing%2C%20with%20audio%20cutting%20in%20and%20out.%20But%20again%2C%20this%20could%20have%20been%20related%20to%20WiFi%20issues%20at%20Samsung's%20facility%20rather%20than%20the%20TV%20itself.%20I'll%20revisit%20this%20feature%20after%20spending%20more%20time%20with%20the%20S95H%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271810d7b-6515-478c-9704-b7ba967bb3e2%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Samsung%20S95H%20OLED%20TV%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221486%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Samsung%20S95H%20OLED%20TV%20hanging%20on%20a%20wall%20in%20a%20living%20room%20setup%20with%20an%20image%20of%20the%20ocean%20and%20a%20sunset%20on%20screen.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efc1a33fecbb42897a4af8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221114%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20S95H%20is%20easily%20one%20of%20the%20most%20impressive%20TVs%20Samsung%20has%20released%20so%20far.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126380930nb-20%