l%20Premium%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126379539ix-20%26h%3Deee3b2fb03decb55d514c2bb509c2c2596ae0a5c38e7888741b988dac6c62adb%26postID%3D69ef82c8215b3a0a3c832fa0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-dna-test%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fwisdom-panel-premium-breed%252Fdp%252F249945%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20at%20Chewy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20European%20breeds%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKoko%20Genetics%20Advanced%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126379539ix-20%26h%3Db2474901fbc7374b9da17bc1b9cf8eb413797e3414ff12749b2cf62dcb1393df%26postID%3D69ef82c8215b3a0a3c832fa0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-dna-test%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fkoko-genetics-advanced-plus-dog-dna%252Fdp%252F1494230%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20at%20Chewy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d28fa7ab-ade7-471f-a89f-de706b5e7d4e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20evaluated%20dog%20DNA%20tests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20evaluate%20dog%20DNA%20tests%2C%20we%20chose%20kits%20from%20seven%20popular%20companies%20and%20tested%20them%20across%20two%20households.%20Senior%20pets%20editor%20Lisa%20Sabatini%20tested%20the%20kits%20with%20her%20dog%20Homer%2C%20and%20I%20collected%20samples%20from%20my%20dogs%20Bug%20and%20Crocodile.%20Each%20dog%20was%20swabbed%20for%20each%20test%20according%20to%20the%20brand's%20collection%20instructions%20to%20ensure%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20dogs%20are%20shown%20side%20by%20side%3A%20one%20standing%20outdoors%20near%20a%20ladder%20and%20tree%2C%20one%20in%20a%20grassy%20field%20with%20hills%20in%20the%20background%2C%20and%20one%20indoors%20on%20a%20carpet%20looking%20up%20at%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f10fd29244129ecb2f9001%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20three%20DNA%20test%20subjects%2C%20shown%20left%20to%20right%2C%20were%20Crocodile%2C%20Bug%2C%20and%20Homer.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%3B%20Lisa%20Sabatini%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20entered%20minimal%20information%20about%20each%20dog%20when%20we%20registered%20our%20kits.%20To%20minimize%20potential%20bias%2C%20we%20did%20not%20upload%20any%20photographs.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biorxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2023.06.28.546898v1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%202023%20study%20out%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2C%20in%20at%20least%20one%20instance%2C%20a%20canine%20DNA%20testing%20company's%20breed%20prediction%20appeared%20to%20be%20influenced%20by%20a%20submitted%20photo%20rather%20than%20the%20DNA%20sample.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20the%20samples%20by%20mail%2C%20we%20compared%20processing%20times%2C%20the%20consistency%20and%20depth%20of%20our%20breed%20reports%2C%20each%20company's%20database%20size%20and%20transparency%2C%20the%20clarity%20of%20included%20health%20screenings%2C%20relative-matching%20tools%2C%20and%20overall%20user%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20accuracy%20and%20limitations%20of%20commercially%20available%20dog%20DNA%20tests%2C%20I%20also%20interviewed%20experts%20in%20the%20field%20to%20better%20understand%20how%20breed%20databases%20differ%2C%20what%20health%20risks%20canine%20genetics%20can%20really%20reveal%2C%20and%20what%20today's%20canine%20genetic%20science%20can%20(and%20can't)%20reliably%20determine.%20The%20experts%20I%20spoke%20with%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvet.purdue.edu%2Fdirectory%2Fperson.php%3Fid%3D1105%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Kari%20Ekenstedt%2C%20DVM%2C%20PhD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20associate%20professor%20of%20anatomy%20and%20genetics%20at%20the%20Purdue%20University%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%20who%20studies%20inherited%20diseases%20in%20dogs%20and%20is%20a%20former%20consultant%20for%20Wisdom%20Panel%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vet.cornell.edu%2Fdepartments-centers-and-institutes%2Fbaker-institute-animal-health%2Fresearch-baker-institute%2Fmeet-our-faculty%2Fjacquelyn-evans-phd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJacquelyn%20Evans%2C%20PhD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Cornell%20University%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%20whose%20research%20focuses%20on%20genetic%20markers%20of%20canine%20disease%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clivewynne.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClive%20Wynne%2C%20PhD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20behavioral%20scientist%20and%20director%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsychology.asu.edu%2Fresearch%2Flabs%2Fcanine-science-collaboratory-wynne%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanine%20Science%20Collaboratory%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Arizona%20State%20University%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20dog%20DNA%20testing%20company%20builds%20its%20own%20reference%20panel%20using%20an%20original%20pool%20of%20canine%20DNA.%20These%20panels%20typically%20include%20dozens%20to%20hundreds%20of%20purebred%20dogs%20per%20breed%20to%20account%20for%20genetic%20drift%20over%20time.%20Because%20every%20company%20uses%20its%20own%20reference%20panel%20to%20analyze%20your%20dog's%20DNA%2C%20results%20can%20vary%20from%20brand%20to%20brand%2C%20especially%20for%20mixed-breed%20dogs%20with%20complex%20ancestry%2C%20and%20it's%20impossible%20to%20declare%20a%20single%20result%20definitively%20%26quot%3Bcorrect.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20results%20that%20diverged%20significantly%20from%20the%20dominant%20breed%20identified%20by%20multiple%20other%20tests%20raised%20questions%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20details%20on%20what%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20DNA%20test%2C%20how%20we%20evaluated%20the%20strength%20of%20breed%20results%20and%20clarity%20of%20health%20screenings%2C%20and%20other%20frequently%20asked%20questions%2C%20scroll%20to%20the%20end%20of%20this%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3c9610e-ec00-47e6-92a2-b2a508edc229%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20overall%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20overall%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126379539ix-20%26h%3D4c77a956badbaf79650cf2ef20211154e916ebe1316810b4f617043ceab6ed0b%26postID%3D69ef82c8215b3a0a3c832fa0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-dna-test%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fembark-breed-identification-health%252Fdp%252F167898%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmbark%20Breed%20and%20Health%20Dog%20DNA%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20delivered%20the%20most%20comprehensive%20results.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOf%20the%20seven%20tests%20we%20ran%20on%20Homer%2C%20Bug%2C%20and%20Crocodile%2C%20Embark%20produced%20the%20clearest%20breed%20breakdowns%20and%20the%20most%20detailed%20health%20screening%20data%20%E2%80%94%20all%20presented%20in%20an%20intuitive%2C%20easy-to-navigate%20dashboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmbark%20has%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20breed%20reference%20panels%20of%20any%20test%20we%20evaluated%2C%20and%20it%20shows%20in%20the%20results.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20company%20says%20its%20reference%20panel%20includes%20over%2031%2C000%20dogs%20across%20more%20than%20400%20breeds%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20comprehensive%20we%20tested.%20The%20extra%20breeds%20in%20its%20database%20actually%20showed%20up%20in%20our%20results.%20One%20of%20our%20dogs%2C%20Bug%2C%20was%20identified%20as%2028%25%20black%20mouth%20cur%2C%20a%20rarer%20Southern%20breed%20that%20five%20of%20our%20seven%20tests%20don't%20include%20in%20their%20databases.%20This%20identification%20may%20help%20explain%20certain%20physical%20traits%20that%20we%20didn't%20find%20with%20the%20breed%20results%20from%20other%20tests%2C%20such%20as%20Bug's%20curly%20tail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmbark%20also%20has%20village%20and%20street%20dogs%20genotyped%20in%20its%20reference%20panel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20includes%2059%20village%20dog%20populations.%20These%20dogs%20live%20outdoors%20without%20owners%20and%20are%20genetically%20distinct%20from%20standard%20breeds.%20This%20may%20produce%20more%20accurate%20results%20for%20dogs%20with%20international%20ancestry%2C%20though%20it%20likely%20doesn't%20benefit%20most%20US-based%20mixed-breeds%20much%2C%20Ekenstedt%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20delivers%20clear%2C%20thoughtfully%20structured%20breed%20results%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Embark's%20breed%20reports%20are%20straightforward%20and%20easy%20to%20navigate%2C%20with%20simple%20color-coding%20and%20a%20well-organized%20interface%20that%20lets%20you%20dig%20deeper%20if%20you%20want%20more%20information.%20Unlike%20Wisdom%20Panel%2C%20which%20includes%20additional%20context%20like%20breed%20group%20category%20(herding%2C%20sporting%2C%20guard%2C%20for%20example)%20and%20photo%20galleries%20for%20each%20group%2C%20Embark%20focuses%20on%20the%20essentials%20with%20a%20straightforward%20breed%20breakdown%20with%20concise%20descriptions%20and%20key%20stats%20like%20average%20weight%20and%20lifespan.%20I%20also%20appreciate%20that%20it%20groups%20distant%20breed%20ancestry%20into%20a%20single%20%26quot%3BSupermutt%26quot%3B%20category%2C%20with%20the%20option%20to%20explore%20in%20more%20detail.%20Ekenstedt%20says%20that%20this%20is%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Bresponsible%26quot%3B%20approach%2C%20since%20breeds%20appearing%20as%205%25%20or%20less%20are%20likely%20very%2C%20very%20far%20back%20in%20the%20dog's%20family%20tree%20and%20difficult%20to%20attribute%20with%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20DNA%20test%20report%20showing%20breed%20mix%20percentages%2C%20genetic%20stats%2C%20and%20a%20chromosome%20breakdown%20chart.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efbdd6367066d7c29719e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmbark%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20tests%20to%20include%20Black%20Mouth%20Cur%20in%20Bug's%20breed%20makeup.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmbark's%20health%20screening%20is%20notably%20thorough%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20The%20test%20screens%20for%20more%20than%20270%20genetic%20health%20conditions%20(274%20conditions%20when%20we%20tested%20in%20December%202025)%2C%20and%20the%20results%20are%20organized%20into%20%26quot%3BClear%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BNotable%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BAt%20Risk%26quot%3B%20categories%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20information%20easier%20to%20interpret%20without%20feeling%20alarmist.%20The%20report%20includes%20plain-language%20explanations%20and%20scientific%20citations%20that%20help%20make%20complex%20genetic%20information%20more%20approachable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20test%20also%20generates%20an%20Allergy%20Risk%20score%20for%20potential%20food%20and%20environmental%20sensitivities.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEvans%20says%20this%20can%20be%20helpful%20to%20share%20with%20your%20veterinarian%20if%20your%20dog%20develops%20common%20symptoms%20of%20allergies%20like%20itchiness%20or%20ear%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmbark%20is%20one%20of%20only%20two%20tests%20that%20allow%20users%20to%20send%20health%20results%20directly%20to%20a%20veterinarian%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20step%20experts%20recommend%20before%20making%20decisions%20based%20on%20the%20report.%20For%20Bug%20and%20Crocodile%2C%20the%20tests%20didn't%20report%20any%20genetic%20health%20risks.%20Homer's%20test%20reported%20an%20Increased%20Risk%20for%20Intervertebral%20Disc%20Disease%20(Type%20I).%20%26quot%3BThis%20result%20does%20not%20guarantee%20that%20he%20will%20develop%20IVDD%2C%20and%20many%20dogs%20never%20show%20clinical%20signs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20notes%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20for%20Homer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmbark%20also%20has%20a%20robust%20relative%20finder.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou%20can%20view%20photos%2C%20locations%2C%20breed%20breakdowns%2C%20and%20even%20message%20potential%20canine%20relatives'%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20overall%20user%20experience%20is%20seamless%20from%20activation%20to%20final%20report%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Swabbing%20and%20kit%20registration%20were%20straightforward%2C%20and%20results%20for%20all%20three%20dogs%20arrived%20in%20under%2030%20days.%20Once%20results%20are%20live%20in%20the%20dashboard%2C%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20toggle%20between%20data%20on%20breed%2C%20health%2C%20traits%2C%20and%20relatives%20without%20feeling%20overwhelmed%20%E2%80%94%20no%20small%20feat%20given%20the%20volume%20of%20information%20included%20in%20a%20dog's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223869%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Embark%20dog%20DNA%20test%20kit%20displayed%20with%20its%20box%2C%20instructions%2C%20and%20sample%20collection%20materials%20laid%20out%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efbdb1367066d7c29719e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222902%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Sabatini%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmbark%20has%20a%20strong%20scientific%20reputation%20and%20research%20partnerships.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Founded%20in%20part%20by%20a%20canine%20geneticist%20at%20Cornell%20University%2C%20Embark%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126379539ix-20%26h%3D8f24fd9b1b957cff602419a50fa49f258016b48890b3b70d2964f56ed9e914f8%26postID%3D69ef82c8215b3a0a3c832fa0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-dna-test%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fembarkvet.com%252Fabout%252Fresearch%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollaborates%20with%20veterinary%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20research%20institutions%20to%20refine%20its%20reference%20panel%20and%20contribute%20to%20broader%20genetics%20research.%20That%20investment%20also%20shows%20in%20the%20depth%20and%20transparency%20of%20its%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20an%20expensive%20kit%2C%20but%20worth%20the%20premium.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20our%20testing%2C%20the%20depth%2C%20clarity%2C%20and%20database%20strength%20justify%20its%20higher%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242ae941c-cc2c-4b63-885f-d0d47036320f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20runner-up%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20runner-up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126379539ix-20%26h%3Deee3b2fb03decb55d514c2bb509c2c2596ae0a5c38e7888741b988dac6c62adb%26postID%3D69ef82c8215b3a0a3c832fa0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-dna-test%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fwisdom-panel-premium-breed%252Fdp%252F249945%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWisdom%20Panel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20delivers%20results%20quickly.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20was%20the%20fastest%20of%20the%20tests%20we%20evaluated.%20We%20shipped%20samples%20from%20upstate%20New%20York%20and%20rural%20Colorado%20and%20received%20our%20reports%20within%2011%20to%2013%20days.%20If%20you're%20eager%20for%20answers%20about%20your%20dog's%20background%2C%20that%20shorter%20turnaround%20can%20make%20a%20noticeable%20difference.%20The%20activation%20process%20and%20swabbing%20experience%20were%20also%20straightforward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20breed%20breakdown%20is%20highly%20detailed%20and%20thoughtfully%20presented.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWisdom%20Panel%20tests%20for%20over%20365%20breeds%20(specifically%2C%20368%20in%20our%20December%202025%20reports).%20While%20Embark%20groups%20mixed%20breed%20heritage%20into%20a%20more%20accurate%20%26quot%3BSupermutt%26quot%3B%20category%2C%20Wisdom%20provides%20percentage%20breakdowns%20down%20to%201%25%2C%20with%20very%20little%20grouping%20of%20overlapping%20breeds.%20Technically%2C%20this%20is%20less%20accurate%2C%20and%20Ekenstedt%20says%20any%20heritage%20reported%20below%205%25%20should%20be%20taken%20with%20a%20grain%20of%20salt.%20Still%2C%20hearing%20that%20your%20dog%20is%202%25%20Pomeranian%20or%201%25%20wolf%20can%20be%20fun%2C%20and%20for%20many%20people%2C%20that%20fun%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20dog%20DNA%20testing's%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20also%20like%20how%20Wisdom%20Panel%20organizes%20breed%20results%20into%20herding%2C%20sporting%2C%20guard%2C%20companion%2C%20and%20other%20groups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20see%20at%20a%20glance%20what%20behaviors%20your%20dog%20might%20be%20inclined%20toward.%20That%20said%2C%20this%20is%20largely%20for%20fun%20since%20Wynne%20says%20many%20of%20the%20defining%20traits%20of%20these%20groups%20are%20social%20constructs.%20Trace%20DNA%20amounts%20aside%2C%20Wisdom%20Panel's%20breed%20breakdown%20felt%20largely%20similar%20to%20the%20other%20tests%2C%20and%20I%20appreciated%20that%20its%20breed%20information%20pages%20included%20more%20details%20and%20photos%20of%20dogs%20than%20other%20tests%20we%20evaluated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWisdom%20Panel%20includes%20street%20dog%20populations%20within%20its%20reference%20panel.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20company%20declined%20to%20disclose%20specifics%20about%20its%20reference%20panel%20composition.%20However%2C%20a%20company%20representative%20says%20its%20test%20currently%20detects%20several%20regional%20street%20dog%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wisdompanel.com%2Fen-us%2Fblog%2Fbreed-vs-landrace%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elandrace%20populations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20screens%20for%20almost%20as%20many%20health%20markers%20as%20Embark.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWisdom%20Panel%20currently%20screens%20for%20265%2B%20genetic%20health%20conditions%2C%20just%20shy%20of%20Embark's%20270%2B%20but%20more%20than%20the%20other%20tests%20we%20tried.%20The%20reports%20are%20thorough%20but%20not%20overwhelming%2C%20with%20risk%20levels%20front%20and%20center%2C%20concise%20snippets%20on%20each%20disease%2C%20and%20the%20option%20to%20learn%20more.%20That%20said%2C%20as%20with%20all%20canine%20DNA%20tests%2C%20these%20results%20indicate%20genetic%20risk%2C%20not%20a%20medical%20diagnosis.%20A%20veterinarian%20or%20veterinary%20geneticist%20will%20need%20to%20confirm%20any%20high-risk%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20DNA%20results%20dashboard%20showing%20a%20pet%20identified%20as%20100%25%20Beagle%20along%20with%20ancestry%20highlights%20and%20relative%20matches.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efbe1c367066d7c29719ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Wisdom%20Panel%20dashboard%20is%20simple%20and%20easy%20to%20navigate%2C%20particularly%20for%20Homer%2C%20who%20has%20only%20one%20breed%20in%20his%20ancestry.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Sabatini%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20dashboard%20is%20intuitive%20and%20easy%20to%20navigate%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Breed%2C%20health%2C%20and%20trait%20data%20are%20clearly%20organized%2C%20and%20the%20interface%20makes%20it%20simple%20to%20toggle%20between%20sections%20without%20getting%20lost.%20While%20it%20doesn't%20feel%20quite%20as%20deep%20or%20research-forward%20as%20Embark's%20reporting%2C%20it's%20still%20among%20the%20most%20polished%20and%20user-friendly%20dashboards%20we%20encountered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20can%20find%20and%20connect%20with%20relatives.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Similar%20to%20Embark%2C%20Wisdom%20Panel%20has%20a%20relative%20finder%2C%20letting%20you%20view%20photos%2C%20location%2C%20breed%20breakdowns%2C%20and%20email%20potential%20canine%20relatives'%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWisdom%20Panel%20has%20a%20strong%20scientific%20foundation%20and%20contributes%20to%20ongoing%20genetics%20research.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20addition%20to%20building%20its%20reports%20on%20established%20canine%20genetics%20research%2C%20Wisdom%20Panel's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wisdompanel.com%2Fen-us%2Four-science%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein-house%20research%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20analyzes%20veterinary%20records%20and%20owner%20survey%20data%20to%20better%20understand%20how%20genetics%20influence%20health%20and%20behavior.%20The%20company%20also%20collaborates%20with%20academic%20and%20research%20institutions%20to%20help%20advance%20pet%20genetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223301%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Wisdom%20Panel%20dog%20DNA%20test%20kit%20with%20packaging%2C%20instructions%2C%20and%20a%20swab%20laid%20out%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efc0a2367066d7c2971a0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222476%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Sabatini%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20nearly%20as%20strong%20as%20Embark%2C%20and%20slightly%20more%20affordable%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Wisdom%20Panel%20is%20an%20excellent%20test%20that%20narrowly%20missed%20our%20top%20spot.%20In%20side-by-side%20testing%20with%20three%20dogs%2C%20it%20delivered%20detailed%20breed%20and%20health%20results%20for%20about%20%2440%20less%20than%20Embark%20and%20with%20a%20faster%20turnaround.%20However%2C%20its%20smaller%20breed%20database%20and%20less%20nuanced%20breed%20grouping%20give%20Embark%20a%20slight%20edge%20for%20testing%20rescue%20and%20mixed-breed%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c374141-609b-427d-a6f8-c2511b6d4fcd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20European%20breeds%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20European%20breeds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126379539ix-20%26h%3Db2474901fbc7374b9da17bc1b9cf8eb413797e3414ff12749b2cf62dcb1393df%26postID%3D69ef82c8215b3a0a3c832fa0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-dna-test%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fkoko-genetics-advanced-plus-dog-dna%252Fdp%252F1494230%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKoko%20Genetics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20has%20a%20European-dominant%20database%20that's%20especially%20compelling%20for%20international%20rescues.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Spain-based%20Koko%20Genetics%20is%20built%20on%20a%20reference%20panel%20of%2030%2C000%20dogs%20across%20more%20than%20400%20breeds%20largely%20from%20Europe%2C%20so%20its%20results%20can%20look%20dramatically%20different%20from%20US-based%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKoko%20matched%20the%20dominant%20breeds%20found%20in%20our%20US%20tests%20but%20also%20identified%20additional%20breeds%20that%20may%20better%20reflect%20dogs%20with%20overseas%20ancestry.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20our%20testing%2C%20the%20dominant%20breeds%20of%20our%20dogs%20(beagle%3B%20poodle%20and%20Siberian%20husky%3B%20German%20shepherd%20and%20Staffordshire%20terrier)%20remained%20consistent%20with%20our%20US-based%20test%20results.%20However%2C%20Koko%20surfaced%20many%20European%2C%20Asian%2C%20and%20South%20American%20village%20and%20regional%20breed%20matches%20that%20didn't%20appear%20in%20most%20US-centric%20databases%2C%20such%20as%20Basset%20Artesien%20Normand%20and%20Wirehaired%20Slovakian%20Pointer.%20There's%20no%20universal%20canine%20DNA%20database%2C%20so%20it's%20impossible%20to%20call%20one%20result%20definitively%20%26quot%3Bmore%20accurate%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20this%20geographically%20shifted%20database%20may%20better%20reflect%20lineage%20for%20dogs%20adopted%20overseas%20or%20with%20European%20street-dog%20ancestry%2C%20Ekenstedt%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20genetics%20app%20screen%20showing%20breed%20composition%20percentages%20alongside%20detailed%20information%20about%20the%20Dogo%20Argentino%20breed.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efbe42a98bc8fdc096f68a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20enjoyed%20diving%20into%20the%20breed%20analysis%20for%20Croc%2C%20which%20included%20Dogo%20Argentino.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIts%20breed%20analysis%20is%20refreshingly%20exciting%2C%20even%20for%20American%20dogs.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBecause%20modern%20breeds%20share%20overlapping%20ancestry%2C%20US-born%20dogs%20still%20have%20genetic%20relatives%20abroad%2C%20Ekenstedt%20says.%20For%20example%2C%20while%20Wisdom%20Panel%20and%20Embark%20reported%20Bug%20as%20part%20Great%20Pyrenees%2C%20Koko%20classified%20him%20as%20the%20European%20South%20Russian%20shepherd%2C%20most%20likely%20a%20genetically%20related%20herding%20dog%20counterpart.%20It%20may%20not%20feel%20radically%20different%20to%20hear%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kokogenetics.com%2Fen%2Fresults%2Fdog-dna-test-breed%2Ffrench-water-dog%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BFrench%20Water%20Dog%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3BBarbet%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20discovering%20those%20international%20equivalents%20is%20undeniably%20fun.%20I%20now%20happily%20tell%20people%20my%20Supermutt%20pup%2C%20Crocodile%2C%20is%20part%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kokogenetics.com%2Fen%2Fresults%2Fdog-dna-test-breed%2Fkarelian-bear-dog%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKarelian%20Bear%20Dog%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kokogenetics.com%2Fen%2Fresults%2Fdog-dna-test-breed%2Fdogo-argentino%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDogo%20Argentino%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20reports%20are%20engaging%20but%20more%20technical.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBreed%20results%20are%20clearly%20presented%20with%20detailed%20background%20information%20on%20each%20breed's%20history%2C%20traits%2C%20and%20characteristics.%20The%20health%20report%20is%20straightforward%2C%20marking%20genetic%20conditions%20as%20%26quot%3Bvariant%20absent%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bpresent.%26quot%3B%20But%20the%20explanations%20lean%20scientific%20and%20are%20less%20approachable%20than%20those%20from%20other%20reports%2C%20which%20can%20make%20positive%20findings%20feel%20more%20intimidating%20even%20though%20genetic%20risk%20isn't%20a%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20logistical%20drawbacks.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Koko%20Genetics%20took%20the%20longest%20of%20any%20company%20to%20deliver%20our%20dogs'%20results%2C%20about%2060%20days%20across%20the%20board.%20The%20kit%20also%20doesn't%20include%20a%20printed%20prepaid%20return%20label.%20You%20must%20register%20your%20kit%20first%20and%20print%20the%20prepaid%20label%20yourself%2C%20which%20can%20delay%20the%20process%20further.%20I%20also%20found%20it%20frustrating%20that%20you%20can't%20register%20multiple%20dogs%20and%20tests%20under%20the%20same%20account%2C%20and%2C%20despite%20having%20relative%20tracking%2C%20we%20didn't%20find%20any%20connections%20for%20our%20three%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222689%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20DNA%20test%20kit%20with%20instructions%2C%20envelopes%2C%20and%20a%20buccal%20swab%20collection%20packet%20arranged%20on%20a%20white%20surface.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efc1f3367066d7c2971a17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222017%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Sabatini%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKoko%20Genetics%20has%20a%20solid%20scientific%20reputation.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Its%20parent%20company%2C%20tellmeGen%2C%20is%20a%20well-respected%2C%20commercial%20genetic%20testing%20company%2C%20and%20its%20pet%20branch%20utilizes%20established%20and%20widely%20accepted%20science%20to%20back%20its%20canine%20health%20reports.%20The%20company%20doesn't%20formally%20promote%20any%20academic%20partnerships%20the%20way%20some%20competitors%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20best%20used%20as%20a%20complementary%20or%20situational%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20For%20US-born%20dogs%20that%20most%20likely%20have%20common%20American%20breed%20mixes%2C%20Koko%20Genetics'%20European-focused%20database%20may%20feel%20less%20comprehensive%20and%20relatable%20than%20Wisdom%20Panel%20and%20Embark.%20But%2C%20if%20you%20have%20the%20money%2C%20it's%20a%20fun%20and%20enlightening%20second%20test%20to%20shine%20more%20light%20on%20your%20original%20results.%20And%20for%20internationally%20adopted%20dogs%2C%20Koko%20Genetics%20fills%20a%20meaningful%20gap%20that%20most%20US-based%20tests%20don't%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d62c268d-880e-4cea-a21d-9bb1a0c3cb0f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20can%20a%20dog%20DNA%20test%20really%20tell%20you%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20a%20dog%20DNA%20test%20really%20tell%20you%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20tests%20will%20use%20DNA%20to%20report%20some%20combination%20of%20a%20dog's%20breed%20makeup%2C%20genetic%20health%20risks%2C%20physical%20traits%2C%20behavioral%20traits%2C%20and%20potentially%20the%20dog's%20genetic%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreed%20analysis%20is%20accurate%2C%20but%20it's%20relative%20to%20what%20DNA%20is%20already%20in%20the%20company's%20database.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEach%20test%20compares%20your%20dog's%20DNA%20to%20a%20company's%20proprietary%20reference%20panel%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20purebred%20dogs%20whose%20DNA%20was%20used%20to%20define%20each%20breed's%20genetic%20profile%2C%20such%20as%20a%20labrador%20or%20a%20poodle.%20The%20reliability%20of%20your%20dog's%20breed%20breakdown%20depends%20largely%20on%20the%20size%20of%20the%20test's%20reference%20panel%20and%20how%20many%20breeds%20the%20company%20counts%20in%20its%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenetic%20health%20risks%20are%20similarly%20accurate%2C%20but%20they%20definitely%20aren't%20comprehensive%20or%20definitive.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERather%20than%20each%20brand%20having%20its%20own%20reference%20panel%20like%20with%20breeds%2C%20there%20is%20a%20universal%20research%20body%20of%20specific%20gene%20mutations%20that%20have%20been%20linked%20with%20certain%20diseases.%20Each%20brand's%20health%20analysis%20compares%20your%20dog's%20DNA%20to%20these%20known%20variants.%20Most%20disease-related%20gene%20variants%20are%20breed-specific%2C%20meaning%20the%20disease%20arose%20within%20that%20breed%20and%20you%20won't%20see%20the%20variant%20in%20other%20breeds%2C%20Ekenstedt%20says.%20It's%20also%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20these%20mutations%20point%20to%20a%20higher%20risk%2C%20not%20a%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tests%20aim%20to%20be%20as%20comprehensive%20as%20possible%2C%20but%20Ekenstedt%20says%20they%20can't%20truly%20be%20comprehensive.%20Evans%20agrees%2C%20adding%20that%20not%20all%20disease-causing%20mutations%20have%20been%20identified%20by%20researchers%2C%20so%20a%20negative%20test%20result%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20a%20dog%20will%20never%20develop%20that%20disease.%20It's%20more%20so%20that%20a%20variant%20match%2C%20or%20marker%20of%20an%20increased%20risk%2C%20is%20something%20you%20should%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20with%20your%20veterinarian.%20This%20is%20especially%20important%20if%20your%20dog%20is%20a%20carrier%20of%20a%20gene%20like%20MDR1%20(covered%20by%20most%20dog%20DNA%20tests)%2C%20which%20affects%20how%20sensitive%20a%20dog%20is%20to%20certain%20medications.%20Ekenstedt%20says%20MDR1%20is%20most%20common%20in%20collies%20and%20shepherds%2C%20but%20can%20appear%20in%20other%20breeds%2C%20and%20that%20just%20one%20copy%20of%20this%20gene%20can%20make%20a%20dog%20more%20sensitive.%20So%20it's%20very%20important%20you%20tell%20your%20vet%20if%20your%20dog%20tested%20positive%20as%20%26quot%3Bat%20risk%26quot%3B%20or%20as%20a%20carrier%20for%20this%20gene%20variant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBehavior%20and%20personality%20traits%20reports%20are%20less%20reliable.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20for%20predicted%20behavioral%20and%20personality%20traits%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC5487251%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%20some%20canine%20behavior%20may%20be%20genetic%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20propensity%20for%20fetching%20or%20pointing%2C%20fear%20of%20loud%20noises.%20However%2C%20a%202022%20study%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fscience.abk0639%3Fadobe_mc%3DMCMID%253D84642491739088231094049347991384876828%257CMCORGID%253D242B6472541199F70A4C98A6%252540AdobeOrg%257CTS%253D1651162390%26_ga%3D2.218466969.1066386900.1651162373-689641651.1609118629%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScience%3C%2Fa%3E%20surveyed%20owners%20of%20more%20than%2018%2C385%20dogs%2C%20both%20purebred%20and%20mixed-breed%2C%20and%20found%20that%20dogs%20of%20the%20same%20breed%20behaved%20very%20differently%20across%20all%20breed%20types.%20%26quot%3BBehavior%20is%20not%20like%20fur%20color%2C%26quot%3B%20Wynne%20says.%20Our%20genes%20play%20some%20role%2C%20he%20says%2C%20but%20the%20majority%20of%20personality%20and%20behavior%20is%20based%20on%20early%20and%20late%20life%20experience.%20Still%2C%20you%20might%20find%20some%20interesting%20nuggets%20in%20your%20pup's%20personality%20analysis.%20For%20our%20dogs%2C%20the%20results%20were%20accurate%20to%20our%20perceptions%20about%2050%25%20to%2080%25%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0595554-18b2-4217-9bb3-aa3ce90a4b60%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20DNA%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20dog%20DNA%20tests%20should%20do%20more%20than%20identify%20your%20dog's%20breed%20mix%20and%20screen%20for%20potential%20health%20risks.%20They%20should%20also%20be%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20continue%20to%20provide%20value%20after%20your%20results%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReference%20panel%20and%20breed%20database%20size%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEach%20dog%20DNA%20testing%20company%20uses%20its%20own%20internal%20reference%20panel%20to%20compare%20your%20dog's%20DNA%20against.%20That%20means%20the%20size%2C%20geographic%20diversity%2C%20and%20transparency%20of%20a%20company's%20reference%20panel%20and%20breed%20database%20matters%20more%20than%20anything%20else.%20Look%20for%20a%20brand%20that%20not%20only%20has%20at%20least%20300%20breeds%20in%20its%20database%2C%20but%20that%20is%20also%20transparent%20about%20how%20many%20dogs%20it's%20tested.%20Our%20top%20pick%2C%20Embark%2C%20has%20a%20database%20of%20over%20400%20breeds%2C%20a%20reference%20panel%20of%20more%20than%2031%2C000%20dogs%2C%20and%20has%20analyzed%202.9%20million%20dogs%20worldwide.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20least%20consistent%20results%20in%20our%20testing%20came%20from%20DNA%20My%20Dog%2C%20which%20has%20350%20breeds%20across%2024%2C000%20dogs%20in%20their%20reference%20panel%20and%20has%20tested%20over%20a%20million%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeaningful%20health%20screening%20reports%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20tests%20advertise%20200-plus%20genetic%20health%20conditions%2C%20but%20what%20really%20matters%20is%20how%20those%20results%20are%20explained.%20Look%20for%20clear%20risk%20categories%20and%20science-backed%20citations.%20Remember%3A%20Genetic%20markers%20indicate%20risk%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20a%20diagnosis.%20Dog%20DNA%20tests%20aren't%20a%20substitute%20for%20an%20evaluation%20by%20your%20veterinarian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETurnaround%20time%20and%20ease%20of%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Results%20can%20take%20anywhere%20from%20two%20weeks%20to%20two%20months.%20If%20you're%20eager%20for%20answers%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20after%20adopting%20a%20new%20dog%20%E2%80%94%20processing%20time%20may%20matter.%20Kit%20activation%2C%20swabbing%20instructions%2C%20prepaid%20return%20shipping%2C%20and%20the%20clarity%20of%20the%20online%20dashboard%20all%20shape%20the%20overall%20experience%20more%20than%20you%20might%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelatives%20finder%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20feature%20isn't%20necessary%2C%20but%20it%20is%20fun%20to%20see%20if%20your%20pup%20has%20siblings%2C%20cousins%2C%20or%20more%20distant%20relatives.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20familial%20matches%20are%20specific%20to%20each%20database.%20Also%2C%20some%20brands%20just%20show%20you%20a%20small%20picture%20and%20name%20of%20dogs%20whose%20DNA%20is%20close%20to%20your%20own%20pups%2C%20while%20others%2C%20like%20Embark%2C%20let%20you%20dive%20deeper%20into%20the%20relative's%20profile%20and%20even%20message%20their%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommitment%20to%20advancing%20canine%20genetic%20research%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20may%20be%20worth%20considering%20the%20added%20value%20of%20buying%20a%20test%20that%20contributes%20to%20canine%20research%20long-term.%20Some%20companies%20use%20aggregated%20data%20to%20contribute%20to%20broader%20academic%20research.%20Companies%20may%20collaborate%20with%20veterinary%20schools%20or%20publish%20findings%20to%20help%20expand%20what%20we%20collectively%20understand%20about%20canine%20health%2C%20disease%20risk%2C%20and%20breed%20history.%20Just%20be%20sure%20the%20company%20is%20transparent%20about%20data%20privacy%20and%20how%20your%20dog's%20genetic%20information%20can%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFuture%20benefits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Dog%20DNA%20tests%20are%20constantly%20being%20optimized%2C%20from%20new%20dogs%20being%20entered%20into%20its%20database%20to%20new%20research%20linking%20specific%20gene%20mutations%20to%20specific%20health%20risks.%20The%20best%20dog%20DNA%20tests%20will%20add%20value%20beyond%20the%20initial%20test%3B%20they'll%20update%20you%20in%20the%20months%20and%20years%20after%20your%20dog's%20analysis%20to%20alert%20you%20to%20new%20relatives%20in%20their%20database%20or%20new%20health%20risks.%20Our%20top%20two%20picks%2C%20Wisdom%20Panel%20and%20Embark%2C%20both%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%20vs.%20value%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Dog%20DNA%20tests%20typically%20range%20from%20%24100%20to%20%24200.%20The%20cheapest%20option%20isn't%20always%20the%20best%20value%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20breed%20database%20is%20limited%20or%20the%20health%20screening%20is%20shallow.%20A%20slightly%20higher%20upfront%20cost%20can%20translate%20to%20more%20comprehensive%2C%20actionable%20insights%2C%20particularly%20for%20mixed-breed%20or%20internationally%20adopted%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f271a150-461f-449f-98c3-a13e39f05c6e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20evaluated%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20evaluated%20the%20best%20dog%20DNA%20tests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20gently%20holds%20a%20dog's%20snout%20while%20using%20a%20swab%20to%20collect%20a%20sample%20from%20its%20mouth.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f116279244129ecb2f906f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDNA%20is%20collected%20from%20Bug%20using%20the%20swab%20included%20in%20the%20Embark%20kit.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20canine%20DNA%20test%20can%20provide%20completely%20definitive%20answers%20about%20breed%20ancestry%20or%20health%20risks.%20When%20evaluating%20the%20best%20dog%20DNA%20tests%2C%20we%20focused%20on%20factors%20that%20most%20affect%20how%20useful%20the%20results%20are%20for%20pet%20owners.%20These%20include%20the%20size%20and%20diversity%20of%20each%20company's%20database%2C%20scientific%20transparency%2C%20consistency%20of%20breed%20results%20across%20brands%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20reports%20provided%20clear%2C%20actionable%20insights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20not%20score%20tests%20based%20on%20the%20accuracy%20of%20their%20health%20screenings%20because%20our%20three%20dogs%20have%20no%20known%20diseases.%20We%20also%20did%20not%20measure%20the%20reliability%20of%20behavioral%20trait%20predictions.%20As%20canine%20behavioral%20scientist%20Wynne%20says%2C%20a%20dog's%20personality%20and%20tendencies%20are%20shaped%20far%20more%20by%20environment%20and%20life%20experiences%20than%20by%20genetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20the%20best%20dog%20DNA%20tests%20worth%20using%2C%20we%20evaluated%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESample%20collection%2C%20kit%20registration%2C%20and%20processing%20time%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20assessed%20how%20simple%20the%20sample%20collection%20and%20mailing%20process%20was%2C%20including%20whether%20the%20instructions%20were%20clear%2C%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20register%20the%20kit%2C%20and%20if%20a%20prepaid%20return%20label%20was%20included.%20We%20also%20tracked%20how%20long%20the%20results%20took%20to%20arrive.%20Tests%20that%20returned%20results%20within%20a%20few%20weeks%20scored%20higher%2C%20while%20those%20taking%20longer%20than%20five%20weeks%20scored%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%20of%20reference%20panel%20and%20breed%20database%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Each%20company%20builds%20a%20reference%20panel%20%E2%80%94%20a%20collection%20of%20purebred%2C%20pedigreed%20dogs%20whose%20DNA%20helps%20define%20the%20genetic%20profile%20of%20each%20breed.%20Your%20dog's%20DNA%20sample%20is%20compared%20against%20this%20panel%20to%20find%20its%20closest%20matches.%20Companies%20also%20maintain%20breed%20databases%2C%20which%20refer%20to%20the%20total%20number%20of%20breeds%20included%20in%20their%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20the%20larger%20and%20more%20diverse%20a%20company's%20database%2C%20the%20more%20accurately%20it%20can%20compare%20your%20dog's%20DNA.%20As%20Ekenstedt%20explains%2C%20the%20DNA%20of%20a%20specific%20dog%20breed%20changes%20every%20generation%20through%20a%20process%20called%20%26quot%3Bgenetic%20drift%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20is%20a%20small%20but%20notable%20difference%20in%20the%20DNA%20between%20dogs%20of%20the%20same%20breed%20that%20are%20bred%20for%20different%20purposes%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20a%20Labrador%20bred%20for%20show%20versus%20field%20trials%2C%20bomb%20detection%2C%20guide%20work%2C%20or%20companionship.%20Because%20of%20this%20variation%2C%20databases%20that%20include%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20dogs%20within%20each%20breed%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20greater%20number%20of%20breeds%20overall%2C%20tend%20to%20produce%20more%20accurate%20breed%20analyses%20for%20the%20average%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelative%20accuracy%20of%20breed%20makeup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Since%20we%20tested%20the%20same%20three%20dogs%20across%20seven%20different%20DNA%20tests%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20compare%20how%20consistent%20the%20breed%20results%20were%20from%20company%20to%20company.%20We%20also%20evaluated%20whether%20the%20breed%20breakdown%20aligned%20with%20what%20we%20know%20about%20each%20dog's%20appearance%2C%20background%2C%20and%20the%20few%20behaviors%20known%20to%20be%20strongly%20breed-linked%2C%20such%20as%20pointing%20or%20herding.%20Consistency%20across%20multiple%20tests%20carried%20significant%20weight%20in%20our%20scoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20health%20markers%20screened%20for%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Hundreds%20of%20genetic%20variants%20are%20associated%20with%20different%20canine%20diseases.%20While%20no%20single%20test%20screens%20for%20all%20of%20them%2C%20we%20awarded%20higher%20scores%20to%20tests%20that%20analyze%20a%20larger%20number%20of%20health%20markers%20and%20clearly%20explain%20what%20those%20findings%20mean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFollow-up%20tools%20and%20information%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20For%20health-related%20results%20in%20particular%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20whether%20companies%20offered%20helpful%20resources%2C%20such%20as%20educational%20materials%2C%20tools%20to%20share%20results%20with%20a%20veterinarian%2C%20and%20guidance%20on%20next%20steps.%20Tests%20that%20presented%20results%20in%20a%20clear%2C%20practical%20way%20scored%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDNA%20relatives%20finders%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20dog%20DNA%20services%20can%20identify%20genetic%20relatives%20within%20their%20databases.%20We%20evaluated%20how%20robust%20these%20family-matching%20features%20were%20and%20how%20much%20useful%20context%20they%20provided%2C%20including%20details%20like%20a%20relative%20dog's%20breed%20analysis%2C%20location%2C%20and%20the%20option%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20dog's%20guardian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ed0859a-5dcd-4794-b6ca-b5d2d1816315%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Dog%20DNA%20tests%20compared%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDog%20DNA%20tests%20compared%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Dog%20DNA%20tests%20compared%5C%22%3EIn%20November%20and%20December%202025%2C%20we%20tried%20seven%20different%20DNA%20tests%20with%20our%20dogs%3A%20Embark%2C%20Wisdom%20Panel%2C%20Koko%20Genetics%2C%20Basepaws%2C%20Know%20Your%20Pet%20DNA%20by%20Ancestry%2C%20DNA%20My%20Dog%2C%20and%20Orivet.%20Below%2C%20I've%20compiled%20each%20company's%20basic%20testing%20details%2C%20along%20with%20my%20assessment%20of%20the%20breed%20reports%20we%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgrou