20received%20and%20processed.%20A%20company%20representative%20says%20the%20issue%20occurred%20during%20the%20time%20when%20the%20company%20was%20transitioning%20from%20a%20Florida%20shipping%20address%20to%20one%20in%20Tennessee%20and%20that%20the%20mail%20forwarding%20system%20did%20not%20function%20properly.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223420ff2c-3e2b-49cc-9bf9-59d45755bbc7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDog%20DNA%20test%20FAQs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20vets%20recommend%20dog%20DNA%20tests%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDog%20DNA%20tests%20can%20be%20a%20useful%20tool%20for%20identifying%20whether%20your%20dog%20may%20be%20at%20risk%20for%20certain%20inherited%20diseases.%20Evans%20says%20this%20information%20can%20allow%20for%20earlier%20screening%2C%20routine%20monitoring%20by%20veterinarians%2C%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20earlier%20treatment%20with%20better%20outcomes.%20However%2C%20Evans%20points%20out%20that%20these%20tests%20don't%20screen%20for%20every%20disease.%20Some%20tests%20also%20report%20a%20dog's%20potential%20for%20dog%20developing%20allergies%2C%20which%20Evans%20says%20may%20help%20speed%20up%20diagnosis%20for%20minor%20issues%20like%20itchy%20skin%20and%20hot%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20accurate%20are%20dog%20DNA%20tests%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20dog%20DNA%20tests%20are%20generally%20reliable%20for%20determining%20your%20dog's%20breed%20makeup%2C%20but%20accuracy%20largely%20depends%20on%20the%20size%20and%20diversity%20of%20the%20company's%20reference%20panel.%20The%20tests%20can%20also%20provide%20useful%20insights%20into%20genetic%20health%20risks%20by%20evaluating%20whether%20your%20dog%20carries%20certain%20variants%20linked%20to%20known%20conditions%2C%20though%20they%20shouldn't%20be%20considered%20a%20full%20health%20screening.%20Predictions%20about%20behavior%20or%20personality%20traits%20aren't%20very%20accurate%2C%20since%20those%20characteristics%20are%20influenced%20more%20by%20environment%20and%20life%20experiences%20than%20genetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20I%20share%20my%20dog's%20health%20analysis%20with%20my%20vet%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20veterinarians%2C%20while%20incredibly%20knowledgeable%2C%20don't%20receive%20much%20genetics%20training%2C%20so%20they%20aren't%20going%20to%20be%20extremely%20comfortable%20interpreting%20the%20results%20from%20a%20DNA%20test%2C%26quot%3B%20Ekenstedt%20says.%20If%20your%20dog%20tests%20positive%20for%20certain%20genetic%20variants%2C%20Ekenstedt%20recommends%20reaching%20out%20to%20a%20licensed%20veterinarian%20who's%20also%20a%20genetic%20counselor%20or%20a%20board-certified%20veterinary%20specialist%20in%20the%20health%20area%20of%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-dna-test%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777408794000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef9b103fecbb42897a49bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-dna-test%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20tested%207%20dog%20DNA%20tests%20on%203%20dogs%20to%20compare%20breed%20accuracy%2C%20health%20screening%2C%20and%20speed.%20These%20kits%20delivered%20the%20most%20reliable%20results.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rschultz%40insider.com%20(Rachael%20Schultz%2CJoshua%20Stern)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98American%20Pie%E2%80%99%20Star%20Shannon%20Elizabeth%20Earns%20More%20Than%20%241.2%20Million%20on%20OnlyFans%20in%20First%20Week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777408685000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236732358%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shannon%20Elizabeth%E2%80%99s%20pivot%20to%20OnlyFans%20is%20off%20to%20a%20blockbu