5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehaving%20twins%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20having%20two%20kids%20and%20only%20needing%20to%20be%20pregnant%20once%2C%20but%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20pipe%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20pregnant%2C%20I%20suspected%20almost%20immediately%20that%20it%20was%20twins.%20My%20husband%2C%20David%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20a%20boutique%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-get-pregnant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eultrasound%20studio%3C%2Fa%3E%20near%20our%20home%20in%20LA.%20Almost%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20wand%20touched%20my%20stomach%2C%20the%20technician%20delivered%20that%20infamous%20line%3A%20%26quot%3BDo%20twins%20run%20in%20your%20family%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20healthy%20babies%20are%20a%20blessing%2C%20but%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-a-twin-and-i-had-two-sets-of-twins-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboy-girl%20twins%3C%2Fa%3E%20felt%20even%20more%20rare%20and%20special.%20David%20and%20I%20are%20both%20models%20and%20actors%2C%20so%20we%20also%20knew%20that%20twins%20are%20in%20demand%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20interviewed%20agents%20during%20my%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20signed%20Luca%20and%20Luna%20with%20an%20agent%20within%20their%20first%20days%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202da0bd1-c437-4b09-9ab4-a795609c4b51%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20lots%20of%20regulations%20about%20babies%20in%20film%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20regulations%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchild-actors-grown-up-then-and-now-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echild%20actors%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20especially%20strict%20for%20babies.%20Luckily%2C%20our%20agent%20helped%20us%20figure%20out%20the%20logistics%2C%20including%20obtaining%20work%20permits%20for%20the%20babies%20(which%20required%20clearance%20from%20their%20pediatricians)%20and%20setting%20up%20special%20savings%20accounts%20for%20their%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222987%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Baby%20next%20to%20TV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef5a5ea98bc8fdc096f2e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222240%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDesanka%20Pinder's%20twins%20filmed%20when%20they%20were%20just%20months%20old.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Desanka%20Pinder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELuca%20and%20Luna%20are%20allowed%20on%20location%20for%20only%20two%20hours%20per%20day%20and%20can%20film%20for%20only%2020%20minutes.%20That's%20why%20twins%20are%20so%20popular%20with%20production%20companies%3A%20they%20can%20get%20double%20the%20filming%20time%20while%20coordinating%20with%20only%20one%20family.%20When%20we%20were%20on%20set%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsunburned-girl-the-pitt-hbo-first-tv-role-story-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Pitt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20there%20was%20another%20set%20of%20twin%20babies%20filming%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20twins%20were%20born%20in%20September%20and%20filmed%20their%20first%20scene%20on%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy%26quot%3B%20in%20November.%20They%20did%20another%20scene%20on%20Grey's%20the%20following%20month%2C%20then%20booked%20two%20scenes%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Pitt%26quot%3B%20in%20January%2C%20when%20they%20were%20about%204%20months%20old.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20babies%20were%20filmed%20in%20both%20shows%2C%20but%20Luna%20appeared%20on%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Luca%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Pitt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d311838-e885-4c11-b3ef-25b0c5c17284%5C%22%3EWatching%20my%20son%20film%20with%20Noah%20Wyle%20was%20surreal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20arrive%20on%20set%2C%20we're%20greeted%20by%20the%20on-set%20nurse%20and%20teacher.%20They're%20an%20extra%20set%20of%20protection%20for%20the%20babies%20and%20extra%20hands%20for%20the%20parents.%20They%20helped%20change%20the%20babies%20and%20hold%20them%20while%20David%20and%20I%20took%20care%20of%20the%20paperwork.%20They%20also%20made%20sure%20we%20didn't%20exceed%20the%20twins'%20allocated%20filming%20time.%20It%20seemed%20like%20they%20tracked%20it%20down%20to%20the%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20amazed%20at%20how%20efficient%20filming%20was%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Pitt.%26quot%3B%20We%20were%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20studio%20in%20about%20an%20hour.%20We%20would%20get%20the%20babies%20dressed%20while%20the%20actors%20rehearsed%2C%20then%20bring%20one%20or%20both%20of%20them%20onto%20the%20sound%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDXR26slAMty%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDXR26slAMty%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDXR26slAMty%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Luna%20%26amp%3B%20Luca%20(%40lunaandluca2025)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWatching%20Luca%20film%20a%20scene%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-stars-oppose-paramount-warner-bros-discovery-deal-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENoah%20Wyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Pitt%26quot%3B%20was%20surreal.%20Here%20was%20an%20award-winning%20actor%20delivering%20a%20beautiful%20monologue%20while%20our%20son%20sat%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20Not%20only%20were%20we%20watching%20an%20expert%20at%20the%20top%20of%20his%20game%20practice%20his%20craft%20in%20real%20time%2C%20but%20our%20normally%20talkative%2C%20active%20baby%20fell%20asleep%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20worked%20out%20perfectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb8cd343-f594-4dbb-adb9-e6bb79d2c87f%5C%22%3EThe%20twins%20recently%20did%20a%20commercial%2C%20and%20we%20plan%20to%20film%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20raising%20Luna%20and%20Luca%20in%20LA%2C%20where%20we're%20privileged%20to%20have%20access%20to%20so%20many%20opportunities.%20We%20might%20as%20well%20take%20advantage%20of%20them.%20We%20want%20the%20babies%20to%20be%20as%20successful%20as%20possible%20in%20life%2C%20and%20this%20is%20one%20way%20to%20help%20with%20that.%20It%20also%20helps%20build%20their%20financial%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222543%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parking%20sign%20on%20TV%20set%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef5a943fecbb42897a4759%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221907%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20twins%20have%20already%20filmed%20for%20other%20projects.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Desanka%20Pinder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBringing%20the%20babies%20to%20set%20has%20been%20a%20way%20for%20me%20to%20bridge%20my%20passion%20for%20acting%20with%20parenting.%20Sometimes%20being%20in%20the%20newborn%20trenches%20is%20difficult%2C%20but%20David%20and%20I%20have%20forced%20ourselves%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20Ultimately%2C%20I%20think%20that%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20us%20to%20adjust%20to%20life%20with%20twins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilming%20with%20the%20babies%20has%20reminded%20us%20about%20who%20we%20are%20and%20what%20we%20love%20to%20do.%20We%20have%20amazing%20memories%20of%20being%20on%20set%20together%2C%20and%20we%20will%20have%20this%20unique%20professional%20documentation%20of%20the%20twins'%20babyhood.%20The%20twins%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-land-a-role-in-a-tv-commercial-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efilmed%20a%20big%20commercial%3C%2Fa%3E%20(I%20can't%20say%20for%20whom)%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20they'll%20have%20more%20bookings.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20we're%20all%20still%20having%20fun%2C%20we'll%20keep%20filming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewborn-twins-agent-greys-anatomy-the-pitt-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777405141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef591d367066d7c2971645%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewborn-twins-agent-greys-anatomy-the-pitt-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Desanka%20Pinder%20says%20she%20signed%20her%20newborn%20twins%20with%20an%20agent%20and%20quickly%20booked%20roles%20on%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Pitt.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ceat%20Q4%20profit%20more%20than%20doubles%20on%20global%20push%2C%20revenue%20rises%2023%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777404549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.bu