%2C%22published%22%3A1757215800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496504%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Roundglass%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%E2%80%99%20has%20planted%20over%203%20million%20native%20trees%20across%20Punjab%2C%20restoring%20biodiversity%2C%20improving%20soil%20and%20water%20health%2C%20and%20creating%20thousands%20of%20jobs%20for%20women%20and%20youth.%20Learn%20how%20this%20movement%20is%20improving%20lives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496504%2Froundglass-foundation-the-billion-tree-project-planting-native-trees-in-villages-livelihoods%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%20Turns%20Cashew%20Crop%20Ruined%20By%20Rains%20into%20Sprouts%2C%20Pickles%20%26amp%3B%20More%3B%20Earns%20Rs%2025%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20September%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20produce%20of%20wet%2C%20harvested%20cashews%20was%20in%20front%20of%20Brijith%20Krishnan.%20The%20unseasonal%20rains%20in%20his%20hometown%20in%20Kerala%20had%20ruined%20the%20crop%20again.%20He%20knew%20this%20crop%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20fetch%20him%20any%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%20in%202020%2C%20the%20mechanical%20engineering%20diploma%20holder%20also%20faced%20another%20challenging%20turn%20of%20events%20when%20he%20unexpectedly%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20supervisor%20in%20an%20IT%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496857%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20cashew%20farming%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20a%20traditional%20source%20of%20income%20for%20his%20family%20%E2%80%93%20was%20also%20on%20the%20decline.%20This%20double%20blow%20left%20him%20without%20a%20stable%20income%20source.%20He%20strived%20to%20permanently%20settle%20in%20his%20hometown%20and%20explore%20new%20avenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20keen%20eye%20for%20innovation%20and%20a%20determination%20to%20make%20a%20meaningful%20impact%2C%20he%20observed%20the%20growing%20trend%20towards%20plant-based%20diets%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20vegan%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeveraging%20his%20mechanical%20engineering%20background%20and%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20create%20value%20in%20cashew%20farming%2C%20he%20delved%20into%20the%20unchartered%20territory%20of%20sprouting%20technology%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F17187%2Fyoung-innovator-created-one-kind-cashew-nut-grading-machine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecashew%20nuts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20officially%20launched%20his%20venture%2C%20Eatery%20Malbarikas%2C%20which%20makes%20dishes%20from%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts%20and%20supplies%20to%20major%20food%20supply%20companies%20and%20hotels%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%20