ucing%20millet%20pancakes%2C%20chocolate-flavoured%20dry%20fruit%20laddoos%2C%20and%20involving%20him%20in%20cooking%2C%20we%20turned%20things%20around.%20Within%20months%2C%20he%20began%20asking%20his%20mother%20for%20the%20same%20dishes.%20His%20mood%20improved%2C%20and%20he%20became%20more%20energetic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20has%20observed%20similar%20changes%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20noticed%20improvements%20in%20focus%20and%20sleep%20patterns.%20When%20parents%20swap%20sugar-loaded%20evening%20snacks%20with%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20fruit%20smoothies%2C%20kids%20are%20calmer%20at%20bedtime%20and%20more%20alert%20in%20school.%20The%20difference%20is%20visible%20within%20weeks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGovernment%E2%80%99s%20push%20on%20the%20millet%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20isn%E2%80%99t%20leaving%20this%20revival%20only%20to%20parents.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Government%20successfully%20lobbied%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20declare%202023%20as%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets.%20The%20idea%3A%20fight%20malnutrition%20globally%20while%20supporting%20climate-resilient%20crops%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMid-Day%20meals%20in%20anganwadis%3A%20States%20like%20Karnataka%20and%20Odisha%20now%20serve%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20malt%2C%20bajra%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20jowar%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFarmer%20support%3A%20Incentives%20for%20millet%20cultivation%20and%20processing%20encourage%20rural%20economies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAwareness%20drives%3A%20Millet%20festivals%2C%20recipe%20competitions%2C%20and%20celebrity%20endorsements%20are%20changing%20perceptions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20a%20global%20conference%20hosted%20sessions%20on%20key%20millet-related%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20including%20promotion%20and%20awareness%20among%20producers%2C%20consumers%2C%20and%20other%20stakeholders%3B%20value%20chain%20development%3B%20health%20and%20nutrition%3B%20market%20linkages%3B%20and%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20nutrition%3A%20Building%20food%20relationships%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20both%20experts%20agree%3A%20food%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20forget%20the%20relationship%20children%20have%20with%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanchita.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20grow%20microgreens%20or%20help%20stir%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20batter%2C%20they%20value%20food%20differently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%20echoes%20this%2C%20drawing%20from%20Western%20practices%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20countries%2C%20children%20are%20encouraged%20to%20join%20in%20kitchens.%20Let%20them%20knead%20dough%2C%20cut%20veggies%2C%20or%20make%20pancake%20shapes.%20Even%20if%20the%20kitchen%20gets%20messy%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20likely%20to%20eat%20the%20food%20they%20helped%20make.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPlanting%20seeds%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildhood%20is%20fleeting%2C%20but%20its%20foundations%20last%20a%20lifetime.%20By%20the%20age%20of%20five%2C%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20brain%20is%20already%2090%25%20developed.%20The%20foods%20parents%20offer%20in%20these%20early%20years%20%E2%80%94%20say%20millet%20%3Cem%3Edosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Einstead%20of%20instant%20noodles%2C%20microgreen%20salads%20instead%20of%20fries%20%E2%80%94%20quietly%20shape%20not%20just%20health%2C%20but%20focus%2C%20mood%2C%20and%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microgreens%20in%20food%20grade%20trays%20are%20grown%20in%20controlled%20environment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-304882%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMicrogreens%20in%20food%20grade%20trays%20are%20grown%20in%20controlled%20environment.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20sums%20it%20up%3A%20%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20many%20of%20us%20today%20have%20autoimmune%20conditions.%20A%20lot%20of%20women%20deal%20with%20PCOS%20and%20hormonal%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20much%20of%20it%20linked%20to%20how%20we%20eat.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20give%20parents%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%2C%20it%20would%20be%20to%20stick%20to%20home-cooked%20meals.%20%3Cem%3EDal%3C%2Fem%3E-rice%20is%20great%2C%20but%20with%20gut%20health%20becoming%20such%20a%20challenge%2C%20we%20need%20to%20think%20beyond.%20What%20does%20our%20gut%20ask%20for%3F%20Fibre%20and%20variety.%20So%20yes%2C%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E-rice%20or%20%3Cem%3Edal-roti%3C%2Fem%3E%20daily%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20adding%20foods%20like%20moringa%20and%20millets%2C%20which%20are%20rich%20in%20antioxidants%2C%20can%20strengthen%20the%20gut%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20our%20immune%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%20adds%3A%20%E2%80%9CKids%20today%20are%20smart.%20They%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20healthy%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20attracted%20to%20packaged%20foods.%20Our%20job%20as%20parents%20is%20to%20make%20the%20good%20stuff%20just%20as%20fun%2C%20creative%2C%20and%20irresistible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESave%20this%20cheat%20sheet%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20about%20what%20to%20eat%20and%20what%20to%20include%20in%20your%20kid%E2%80%99s%20diet%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20overwhelming.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20come%20up%20with%20the%20perfect%20cheat%20sheet%20for%20parents%20to%20look%20up%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThree%20easy%20millet%20swaps%20for%20lunchboxes%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReplace%20white%20rice%20with%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20foxtail%20millet%20upma%20for%20a%20filling%20meal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwap%20maida-based%20wraps%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F412561%2Fmillets-summer-cooling-jowar-foxtail-ragi-temperature-diet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejowar%20or%20bajra%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stuffed%20with%20veggies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETry%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20millet%20cookies%20as%20tiffin%20treats%20instead%20of%20packaged%20biscuits.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFive%20quickest%20microgreen%20uses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3